  <body>
    <div>
      <p
        begin="00:00:35.070"
        end="00:00:37.660"><span region="Default">♪ Jika aku ada sayap, aku boleh terbang, oh oh ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:37.660"
        end="00:00:39.920"><span region="Default">♪ Jika tiada, aku cuma akan berjalan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:39.920"
        end="00:00:40.950"><span region="Default">♪ Dalam angin kering ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:40.950"
        end="00:00:42.630"><span region="Default">♪ Itu cara aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:42.630"
        end="00:00:43.700"><span region="Default">♪ Walau ia pelik ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:43.700"
        end="00:00:46.050"><span region="Default">♪ Aku ada misi yang aku kena lakukan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:46.050"
        end="00:00:47.960"><span region="Default">♪ Bagaimana dengan kau? Aku ikuti (dan) ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:47.960"
        end="00:00:50.690"><span region="Default">♪ Dengar kata hati aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:50.690"
        end="00:00:55.720"><span region="Default">♪ Aku tak ada masa nak menangis ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:55.720"
        end="00:00:57.870"><span region="Default">♪ Jahat keliling kita, oh ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:00:58.280"
        end="00:01:03.430"><span region="Default">♪ Kalau asyik fikir betul ke salah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:03.430"
        end="00:01:04.849"><span region="Default">♪ Itu dah salah langkah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:04.860"
        end="00:01:08.340"><span region="Default">♪ Dibawa ombak kuat dan angin ganas ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:08.570"
        end="00:01:10.400"><span region="Default">♪ Kami takkan, takkan sekali-kali ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:10.400"
        end="00:01:12.220"><span region="Default">♪ Kita takkan tumbang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:12.460"
        end="00:01:19.060"><span region="Default">(Wowowowowowowowow…)</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:19.060"
        end="00:01:26.230"><span region="Default">♪ Api marak tak biar aku lari ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:26.830"
        end="00:01:28.610"><span region="Default">♪ Pertarungan kini bermula ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:28.610"
        end="00:01:30.860"><span region="Default">♪ Tiada lagi jalan kembali ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:31.289"
        end="00:01:33.430"><span region="Default">♪ Walau dihantui rasa takut ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:33.430"
        end="00:01:34.780"><span region="Default">♪ Jangan sesekali berpaling lari ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:34.780"
        end="00:01:36.229"><span region="Default">♪ Pertarungan kini bermula ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:36.229"
        end="00:01:38.470"><span region="Default">♪ Tiada lagi jalan kembali ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:38.780"
        end="00:01:42.220"><span region="Default">♪ Hadapinya dengan hati dan jiwa yang kuat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:42.220"
        end="00:01:44.210"><span region="Default">♪ Rasakan semangat yang membara ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:44.210"
        end="00:01:46.039"><span region="Default">♪ Percaya pada semangat membara ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:46.039"
        end="00:01:47.710"><span region="Default">♪ Teruskan, teruskan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:47.710"
        end="00:01:48.800"><span region="Default">♪ Masih terlalu awal untuk berakhir ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:48.800"
        end="00:01:51.160"><span region="Default">Namun, kami tidak akan mengalah!<br/>♪ Masih terlalu awal untuk berakhir ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:01:58.970"
        end="00:02:02.710"><span region="Default">♪ Asal kita bersama, ke mana pun boleh pergi! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:02.710"
        end="00:02:06.610"><span region="Default">♪ Betul! Ini adalah dunia kami! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:06.610"
        end="00:02:10.500"><span region="Default">♪ Walau rasa takut, walau menangis pun ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:10.500"
        end="00:02:12.280"><span region="Default">♪ Jangan risau! Senyumlah! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:12.280"
        end="00:02:14.780"><span region="Default">♪ Awak bukannya bersendirian ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:15.910"
        end="00:02:17.579"><span region="Default">♪ Kita akan dapat! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:17.579"
        end="00:02:19.930"><span region="Default">♪ Senyuman yang bersinar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:19.930"
        end="00:02:23.790"><span region="Default">♪ Sebab itulah harta paling berharga ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:24.420"
        end="00:02:25.660"><span region="Default">♪ Burning Burning ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:25.660"
        end="00:02:26.310"><span region="Default">Mari pergi, Pasukan Pertahanan Kasukabe!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:26.310"
        end="00:02:27.870"><span region="Default">♪ Fighting Fighting ♪<br/>Mari pergi, Pasukan Pertahanan Kasukabe!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:28.660"
        end="00:02:29.880"><span region="Default">India?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:29.880"
        end="00:02:32.130"><span region="Default">Negara yang terkenal dengan kari?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:32.130"
        end="00:02:32.890"><span region="Default">Ya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:33.560"
        end="00:02:35.920"><span region="Default">Setiap tahun di Bandar Mushibai,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:35.920"
        end="00:02:39.700"><span region="Default">daerah Hagashimir, India ada festival hiburan</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:39.700"
        end="00:02:42.230"><span region="Default">dengan nyanyian, tarian dan muzikal.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:42.230"
        end="00:02:43.980"><span region="Default">Wah, hebatnya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:46.020"
        end="00:02:49.079"><span region="Default">Gadis bernama Ariana yang tampil tahun lepas</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:49.079"
        end="00:02:51.420"><span region="Default">kini sangat popular di India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:51.990"
        end="00:02:53.440"><span region="Default">Comelnya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:02:56.550"
        end="00:03:00.640"><span region="Default">Kali ni, sempena meraikan jadi bandar kembar dengan Mushibai,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:00.640"
        end="00:03:04.250"><span region="Default">akan ada Festival Hiburan Kanak-Kanak Kasukabe.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:04.250"
        end="00:03:07.140"><span region="Default">Jika  menang, awak akan dijemput ke India,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:07.140"
        end="00:03:09.260"><span region="Default">dan menari di atas pentas festival sana!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:09.900"
        end="00:03:11.960"><span region="Default">Boleh pergi ke India secara percuma?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:11.960"
        end="00:03:12.570"><span region="Default">Betul!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:12.570"
        end="00:03:14.250"><span region="Default">Kita sebagai Pasukan Pertahanan Kasukabe</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:14.250"
        end="00:03:16.640"><span region="Default">cuba wakili Tadika Futaba!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:16.640"
        end="00:03:18.070"><span region="Default">Itu nampak seronok!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:18.070"
        end="00:03:20.390"><span region="Default">Tapi boleh tak kita lakukannya?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:20.390"
        end="00:03:22.970"><span region="Default">Masao! "Ia mustahil dari awal!"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:22.970"
        end="00:03:25.840"><span region="Default">Seharusnya "Tiada yang mustahil dari awal."</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:25.840"
        end="00:03:30.210"><span region="Default">Aku nak makan kari dengan kakak India yang cantik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:30.210"
        end="00:03:31.980"><span region="Default">Nene pun nak pergi India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:31.980"
        end="00:03:33.050"><span region="Default">Setuju!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:33.050"
        end="00:03:34.780"><span region="Default">Ya, aku juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:34.780"
        end="00:03:35.860"><span region="Default">Okey, dah putus!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:35.860"
        end="00:03:38.320"><span region="Default">Mari pergi ke India bersama-sama!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:38.320"
        end="00:03:39.720"><span region="Default">Yeah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:40.010"
        end="00:03:41.910"><span region="Default">♪ Now the battle begins ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:41.910"
        end="00:03:44.030"><span region="Default">♪ There is no going back ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:44.460"
        end="00:03:46.600"><span region="Default">♪ Even when struck by fear ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:46.600"
        end="00:03:48.000"><span region="Default">♪ Don't turn your back ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:48.000"
        end="00:03:49.400"><span region="Default">♪ Now the battle begins ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:49.400"
        end="00:03:51.470"><span region="Default">♪ There is no going back ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:51.910"
        end="00:03:55.360"><span region="Default">♪ Face it with a strong heart and soul ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:55.360"
        end="00:03:57.380"><span region="Default">♪ Feel the burning fighting spirit ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:57.380"
        end="00:03:59.450"><span region="Default">♪ Believe in the burning fighting spirit ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:03:59.450"
        end="00:04:00.860"><span region="Default">♪ Keep on keep on ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:00.860"
        end="00:04:03.730"><span region="Default">♪ It is still too early to end ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:07.690"
        end="00:04:10.010"><span region="Default">Shin-chan, macam mana dengan latihan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:10.010"
        end="00:04:12.480"><span region="Default">Aku tengah main Piro-Piro ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:12.480"
        end="00:04:14.830"><span region="Default">Asyik latihan saja,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:14.830"
        end="00:04:17.350"><span region="Default">kadang-kadang nak main masak-masak juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:17.350"
        end="00:04:19.360"><span region="Default">Saya ada ujian English hari ini,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:19.360"
        end="00:04:21.120"><span region="Default">kena belajar sikit jugalah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:23.930"
        end="00:04:25.850"><span region="Default">Kamu semua, tengok ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:30.000"
        end="00:04:31.000"><span region="Default">Naan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:33.130"
        end="00:04:34.690"><span region="Default">Itu naan kah?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:34.690"
        end="00:04:36.600"><span region="Default">Ya, ini naan lah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:37.480"
        end="00:04:39.640"><span region="Default">Boleh menari dengan kamu semua di India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:39.640"
        end="00:04:44.040"><span region="Default">Mesti seronok, seronok sangat-sangat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:47.270"
        end="00:04:51.230"><span region="Default">Cuma sekali saja, masa berharga kita.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:52.060"
        end="00:04:53.110"><span region="Default">Betul itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:53.110"
        end="00:04:55.830"><span region="Default">Jika tak menang, kita tak boleh pergi ke India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:55.830"
        end="00:04:57.960"><span region="Default">Ya! Mari kita berlatih lagi!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:04:57.960"
        end="00:05:00.410"><span region="Default">Hei, Kazama. Awak lah yang pemalas.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:00.410"
        end="00:05:01.760"><span region="Default">Itu awak lah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:02.290"
        end="00:05:05.330"><span region="Default">(Festival Hiburan Kanak-Kanak Kasukabe)</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:09.590"
        end="00:05:13.330"><span region="Default">♪ Asal kita bersama, ke mana pun boleh pergi! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:13.330"
        end="00:05:17.240"><span region="Default">♪ Betul! Ini adalah dunia kami ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:17.240"
        end="00:05:21.120"><span region="Default">♪ Walau rasa takut, walau menangis pun ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:21.120"
        end="00:05:22.900"><span region="Default">♪ Jangan risau! Senyumlah! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:22.900"
        end="00:05:25.400"><span region="Default">♪ Awak bukannya bersendirian ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:26.400"
        end="00:05:30.490"><span region="Default">♪ Kita akan dapat! Senyuman yang bersinar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:30.490"
        end="00:05:34.350"><span region="Default">♪ Sebab itulah harta paling berharga ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:35.030"
        end="00:05:36.270"><span region="Default">♪ Burning Burning ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:36.659"
        end="00:05:38.110"><span region="Default">♪ Fighting Fighting ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:42.480"
        end="00:05:43.730"><span region="Default">♪ Burning Burning ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:44.110"
        end="00:05:45.560"><span region="Default">♪ Fighting Fighting ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:50.020"
        end="00:05:51.270"><span region="Default">♪ Burning Burning ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:51.780"
        end="00:05:53.230"><span region="Default">♪ Fighting Fighting ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:05:58.510"
        end="00:05:59.880"><span region="Default">Yay!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:21.910"
        end="00:06:24.430"><span region="Default">Namaste!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:25.080"
        end="00:06:29.210"><span region="Default">(Crayon Shinchan the Movie: Super Hot! The Spicy Kasukabe Dancers)</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:29.210"
        end="00:06:31.040"><span region="Default">♪ Kau ada cahaya superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:31.040"
        end="00:06:32.980"><span region="Default">♪ Di mata aku, kau superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:32.980"
        end="00:06:34.590"><span region="Default">♪ Kamu semua superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:34.590"
        end="00:06:36.700"><span region="Default">♪ Sebab itu semua orang superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:36.700"
        end="00:06:38.600"><span region="Default">♪ Cepat sedar, kau superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:38.600"
        end="00:06:40.240"><span region="Default">♪ Esok kau akan bersinar, superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:40.240"
        end="00:06:42.540"><span region="Default">♪ Duratatata dularararararara ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:42.540"
        end="00:06:43.940"><span region="Default">♪ Semua orang ialah superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:45.030"
        end="00:06:48.770"><span region="Default">♪ Kau sangat kuat, kau sangat bijak ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:48.770"
        end="00:06:53.130"><span region="Default">♪ Kau hensem, kau baik dengan semua ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:53.130"
        end="00:06:54.970"><span region="Default">♪ Pandai menyanyi, pandai melukis ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:54.970"
        end="00:06:56.750"><span region="Default">♪ Takkan putus asa sampai akhir ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:56.750"
        end="00:06:58.580"><span region="Default">♪ Jika semua orang begitu ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:06:58.580"
        end="00:07:00.500"><span region="Default">♪ Dunia pastinya terus berputar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:00.500"
        end="00:07:02.550"><span region="Default">♪ Fikir apa yang cuma kau saja boleh buat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:02.550"
        end="00:07:03.980"><span region="Default">♪ Bukan hal yang kau tak boleh buat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:03.980"
        end="00:07:05.960"><span region="Default">♪ Jadi, percaya pada diri sendiri ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:05.960"
        end="00:07:07.670"><span region="Default">♪ Dan pegang yakin dengan kuat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:07.670"
        end="00:07:09.860"><span region="Default">♪ Kau ni macam berlian, digilap terus bersinar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:09.860"
        end="00:07:11.590"><span region="Default">♪ Tanpa kau, apa-apa pun takkan boleh mula ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:11.590"
        end="00:07:13.430"><span region="Default">♪ Di dunia bernama bumi ni ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:13.430"
        end="00:07:15.280"><span region="Default">♪ Semua orang ialah hero, superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:15.280"
        end="00:07:17.140"><span region="Default">♪ We are superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:17.140"
        end="00:07:18.970"><span region="Default">♪ Semua orang superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:18.970"
        end="00:07:20.810"><span region="Default">♪ Leader, Hero ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:20.810"
        end="00:07:22.700"><span region="Default">♪ We go, superstar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:23.060"
        end="00:07:24.550"><span region="Default">♪ Are you superstar? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:27.420"
        end="00:07:29.420"><span region="Default">Ini adalah… India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:39.270"
        end="00:07:42.210"><span region="Default">Kamu semua berpegangan tangan agar tak tersesat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:53.909"
        end="00:07:58.020"><span region="Default">Bo! Shinnosuke! Hati-hati! Jangan berlari!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:07:58.020"
        end="00:08:00.950"><span region="Default">Hei, Shinnosuke! Tunggu situ!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:07.970"
        end="00:08:09.340"><span region="Default">Ini batu yang bagus!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:16.170"
        end="00:08:19.400"><span region="Default">Himawari, pandainya kamu, boleh ikut sampai ke sini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:19.400"
        end="00:08:21.480"><span region="Default">Hei! Jangan buat begitu, Hima.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:21.900"
        end="00:08:25.020"><span region="Default">Maaflah, sampai datang satu keluarga sekali.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:25.020"
        end="00:08:26.500"><span region="Default">Maaf ya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:27.840"
        end="00:08:28.930"><span region="Default">Tak apa-apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:28.930"
        end="00:08:31.400"><span region="Default">Saya tak boleh nak pantau mereka sendiri.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:31.400"
        end="00:08:33.380"><span region="Default">Adanya kamu ini sangat membantu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:33.380"
        end="00:08:37.169"><span region="Default">Kalau ayah dan ibu aku boleh datang kan bagus…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:37.169"
        end="00:08:40.980"><span region="Default">Ayah ibu aku pun tak dapat cuti.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:40.980"
        end="00:08:42.070"><span region="Default">Aku pun sama.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:42.070"
        end="00:08:44.450"><span region="Default">Orang dewasa ini tak boleh cuti tiba-tiba.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:44.450"
        end="00:08:47.840"><span region="Default">Bagusnya Papa Shin-chan tak ada kerja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:47.840"
        end="00:08:50.170"><span region="Default">Bukannya pakcik tiada kerja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:50.170"
        end="00:08:53.730"><span region="Default">Sebab syarikat tak kisah pun jika ayah tiada.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:53.730"
        end="00:08:54.980"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:54.980"
        end="00:08:58.100"><span region="Default">Hakikat boleh lukakan hati orang tau.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:08:58.780"
        end="00:09:00.690"><span region="Default">Termasuk Shiro juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:00.690"
        end="00:09:02.650"><span region="Default">Shiro ini keluarga kami juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:03.600"
        end="00:09:05.440"><span region="Default">Jadi, siapa pula ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:05.440"
        end="00:09:09.080"><span region="Default">Inilah pemandu pelancong yang akan membawa kita ke Mushibai,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:09.080"
        end="00:09:11.010"><span region="Default">Encik Mhm Uh-huh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:11.010"
        end="00:09:12.970"><span region="Default">Harap dapat bekerjasama.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:12.970"
        end="00:09:14.000"><span region="Default">Mhm.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:14.000"
        end="00:09:15.630"><span region="Default">Uh-huh!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:17.770"
        end="00:09:20.100"><span region="Default">Wah, apa ni?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:20.100"
        end="00:09:21.810"><span region="Default">Ini dipanggil Chai, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:21.810"
        end="00:09:22.860"><span region="Default">Uh-huh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:22.860"
        end="00:09:25.330"><span region="Default">Ia ialah teh susu yang dibuat dengan merebus daun teh</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:25.330"
        end="00:09:27.400"><span region="Default">dan ditambah rempah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:27.400"
        end="00:09:29.600"><span region="Default">Bos tahu banyak pasal ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:29.600"
        end="00:09:31.610"><span region="Default">Sebab saya dah buat kajian dulu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:33.490"
        end="00:09:34.570"><span region="Default">Namaste.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:35.220"
        end="00:09:37.920"><span region="Default">Namaste itu kata sapaan India, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:38.450"
        end="00:09:41.510"><span region="Default">Maksudnya sama seperti "Hello" dan "Selamat tinggal".</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:41.990"
        end="00:09:43.050"><span region="Default">Kazama!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:43.050"
        end="00:09:45.390"><span region="Default">Awak nak lihat "Namaste" istimewa aku?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:45.390"
        end="00:09:47.090"><span region="Default">Namaste istimewa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:47.590"
        end="00:09:50.880"><span region="Default">Bercakap pasal India,<br/>ini adalah gajah India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:50.880"
        end="00:09:52.480"><span region="Default">Gajah India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:52.480"
        end="00:09:54.520"><span region="Default">Namaste!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:54.520"
        end="00:09:56.100"><span region="Default">Gajah dari mana pula itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:56.100"
        end="00:09:57.090"><span region="Default">Bebal.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:09:57.090"
        end="00:09:58.980"><span region="Default">Gajah ini haiwan yang bijak tau!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:01.000"
        end="00:10:04.880"><span region="Default">Saya ketawa kuat sangat sampai<br/>hingus keluar lebih banyak dari biasa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:06.070"
        end="00:10:09.510"><span region="Default">Aku jenis yang guna lagu "Si Gajah" kalau nak cakap benda penting.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:09.520"
        end="00:10:13.170"><span region="Default">Kazama, awak terpijak tahi lembu. Si Gajah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:13.950"
        end="00:10:15.620"><span region="Default">Saya dah terpijak kuat-kuat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:15.620"
        end="00:10:16.860"><span region="Default">Aduhai.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:16.860"
        end="00:10:18.420"><span region="Default">Tak apa, tak apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:18.650"
        end="00:10:20.520"><span region="Default">Mari, biar saya cuci dengan air ya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:20.520"
        end="00:10:23.180"><span region="Default">Itu satu hal biasa di India ini, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:23.180"
        end="00:10:24.500"><span region="Default">Uh-huh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:43.610"
        end="00:10:45.550"><span region="Default">Lihat ini, Bo-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:45.550"
        end="00:10:48.610"><span region="Default">- Bura… bura…<br/>- Buri-buri! Buri-buri! Buri-buri!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:48.610"
        end="00:10:51.230"><span region="Default">Mari guna ini ketika di festival hiburan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:51.230"
        end="00:10:54.230"><span region="Default">- Bura… bura…<br/>- Buri-buri! Buri-buri! Buri-buri!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:10:54.230"
        end="00:10:57.700"><span region="Default">- Bura… bura…<br/>- Buri-buri! Buri-buri! Buri-buri!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:11:57.620"
        end="00:11:58.650"><span region="Default">Kunci?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:11:59.060"
        end="00:12:00.420"><span region="Default">Itu pasti untuk…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:10.110"
        end="00:12:11.620"><span region="Default">Apa benda pula itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:11.620"
        end="00:12:12.700"><span region="Default">Hidung…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:13.540"
        end="00:12:16.060"><span region="Default">punya beg belakang?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:20.050"
        end="00:12:22.150"><span region="Default">Itu sepadan dengan awak, Shin-chan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:26.960"
        end="00:12:29.340"><span region="Default">Saya nak ambil ini! Snooze.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:29.650"
        end="00:12:30.840"><span region="Default">Please.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:32.110"
        end="00:12:34.580"><span region="Default">Sebenarnya saya ambil di sana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:34.580"
        end="00:12:36.590"><span region="Default">(Cuma 100 saja)</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:36.590"
        end="00:12:38.040"><span region="Default">Aku ada duit.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:38.480"
        end="00:12:41.040"><span region="Default">Aku ada seratus juta yen~</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:45.910"
        end="00:12:48.110"><span region="Default">Sila, ambillah semua.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:12:48.110"
        end="00:12:49.850"><span region="Default">Mungkin tak cukup.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:00.960"
        end="00:13:04.470"><span region="Default">Hanagelina Jolie~ nampak begitu bagus!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:04.470"
        end="00:13:06.390"><span region="Default">Hanagelina?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:06.390"
        end="00:13:07.990"><span region="Default">Itu nama hidung ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:07.990"
        end="00:13:10.410"><span region="Default">Awak boleh gunanya bila-bila masa saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:10.410"
        end="00:13:13.610"><span region="Default">Hanagelina itu separuh daripada hidung awak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:14.500"
        end="00:13:15.820"><span region="Default">Terima kasih.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:19.610"
        end="00:13:22.200"><span region="Default">Bila dicantum, ia akan jadi bentuk hati.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:22.200"
        end="00:13:24.080"><span region="Default">Batu berbentuk punggung!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:24.080"
        end="00:13:25.960"><span region="Default">Ya, punggung.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:25.960"
        end="00:13:27.380"><span region="Default">Dan separuh untuk awak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:27.690"
        end="00:13:28.690"><span region="Default">Tak apakah?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:29.230"
        end="00:13:30.900"><span region="Default">Sipi rambutku dari India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:30.900"
        end="00:13:33.100"><span region="Default">Itu cenderamata.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:33.100"
        end="00:13:34.550"><span region="Default">Sama macam.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:34.550"
        end="00:13:36.450"><span region="Default">Macam sama.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:41.270"
        end="00:13:45.830"><span region="Default">♪ Kita akan dapat! Senyuman yang bersinar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:45.830"
        end="00:13:50.000"><span region="Default">♪ Sebab itulah harta paling berharga ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:50.670"
        end="00:13:52.720"><span region="Default">Persembahan akan diadakan lusa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:53.480"
        end="00:13:54.650"><span region="Default">Tak sabarnya saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:55.910"
        end="00:13:57.560"><span region="Default">Akhirnya, kecomelan saya, Nene ini</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:13:57.560"
        end="00:13:59.830"><span region="Default">akan diketahui oleh seluruh dunia!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:00.170"
        end="00:14:01.630"><span region="Default">Yalah itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:01.630"
        end="00:14:03.850"><span region="Default">Saya pula berasa gemuruh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:03.850"
        end="00:14:05.110"><span region="Default">Ini masih awal lagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:05.110"
        end="00:14:06.230"><span region="Default">Jangan risau!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:06.230"
        end="00:14:09.040"><span region="Default">Orang India lagi ramai dari Kasukabe.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:09.040"
        end="00:14:11.050"><span region="Default">Mereka semua akan perhatikan awak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:11.050"
        end="00:14:12.280"><span region="Default">Jangan kata begitu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:13.690"
        end="00:14:17.260"><span region="Default">Saya rasa begitu seronok dapat menari dengan kamu semua!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:24.370"
        end="00:14:25.710"><span region="Default">Alahai.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:26.800"
        end="00:14:28.010"><span region="Default">Saya dah balik.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:28.340"
        end="00:14:29.610"><span region="Default">Awak ada jual apa-apa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:29.830"
        end="00:14:31.230"><span region="Default">Cuma barang promosi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:35.080"
        end="00:14:36.330"><span region="Default">Selamat datang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:46.020"
        end="00:14:47.820"><span region="Default">Kami tengah cari kertas.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:47.820"
        end="00:14:49.150"><span region="Default">Kertas?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:49.150"
        end="00:14:51.590"><span region="Default">Ia nampak seperti tisu biasa saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:51.590"
        end="00:14:53.250"><span region="Default">Tapi kertas itu—</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:53.730"
        end="00:14:55.010"><span region="Default">Menurut tekaan saya,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:14:55.010"
        end="00:14:58.040"><span region="Default">sekarang ia terkunci dalam bekas macam ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:01.890"
        end="00:15:03.570"><span region="Default">Saya tak pernah lihat itu sebelum ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:03.570"
        end="00:15:05.130"><span region="Default">Dan ia tiada dalam kedai ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:05.130"
        end="00:15:06.870"><span region="Default">Nampaknya ia ada di sini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:06.870"
        end="00:15:08.210"><span region="Default">Seperti dijangka, abang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:08.210"
        end="00:15:09.980"><span region="Default">Saya dah kata tiada!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:09.980"
        end="00:15:11.580"><span region="Default">Sibuknya saya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:11.580"
        end="00:15:13.470"><span region="Default">Kamu boleh keluar sekarang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:13.470"
        end="00:15:14.850"><span region="Default">Sia-sia saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:14.850"
        end="00:15:17.150"><span region="Default">Awak tak boleh sembunyikan apa-apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:17.760"
        end="00:15:19.750"><span region="Default">Betul tak, abang?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:36.830"
        end="00:15:39.670"><span region="Default">♪ Beritahu saja kebenarannya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:39.670"
        end="00:15:42.580"><span region="Default">♪ Katakan saja, hal jadi mudah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:42.580"
        end="00:15:45.530"><span region="Default">♪ 3, 2, 1, cuba katakannya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:45.530"
        end="00:15:48.400"><span region="Default">♪ Katakan saja, ia akan rasa lega ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:54.190"
        end="00:15:57.160"><span region="Default">♪ Mari goyang bahu, jom nyanyi? Yeah!♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:57.160"
        end="00:16:00.040"><span region="Default">♪ Mari melangkah, jom menari? Come On! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:00.040"
        end="00:16:06.010"><span region="Default">♪ Bukalah mulut kau dan katakan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:06.010"
        end="00:16:07.440"><span region="Default">♪ Atas ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:08.740"
        end="00:16:11.790"><span region="Default">♪ Atas ke? Kanan ke? Kiri ke? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:11.790"
        end="00:16:14.630"><span region="Default">♪ Tidak, tidak, tidak, tidak! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:14.630"
        end="00:16:17.500"><span region="Default">♪ Sini ke? Situ ke? Atau sana ke? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:17.870"
        end="00:16:20.480"><span region="Default">♪ Tidak, tidak, tidak, tidak! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:20.480"
        end="00:16:26.310"><span region="Default">♪ Kertas itu ialah raksasa rahsia ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:26.310"
        end="00:16:31.310"><span region="Default">♪ Satu-satunya, paling jahat, pelik lagi aneh, ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:31.990"
        end="00:16:34.920"><span region="Default">♪ Mengejutkan dan menggemparkan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:35.220"
        end="00:16:37.920"><span region="Default">♪ Ia tak mungkin ada di situ! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:37.920"
        end="00:16:39.050"><span region="Default">♪ Jadi, ia di mana ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:39.270"
        end="00:16:40.510"><span region="Default">♪ Kertas itu di sini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:42.970"
        end="00:16:43.980"><span region="Default">Tiada!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:44.870"
        end="00:16:46.730"><span region="Default">Saya baru jual barang ini tadi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:47.160"
        end="00:16:48.450"><span region="Default">Dengan siapa awak jual?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:48.450"
        end="00:16:49.490"><span region="Default">Budak luar negara,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:49.490"
        end="00:16:51.350"><span region="Default">seorang yang punggung goyang</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:51.350"
        end="00:16:53.600"><span region="Default">dan seorang yang hingus bergoyang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:53.600"
        end="00:16:55.310"><span region="Default">Punggung goyang?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:55.310"
        end="00:16:56.790"><span region="Default">Hingus bergoyang?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:56.790"
        end="00:16:58.980"><span region="Default">Lebih kurang macam itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:00.690"
        end="00:17:04.210"><span region="Default">Jika "kertas" itu tercucuk masuk ke dalam hidung seseorang…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:05.420"
        end="00:17:08.300"><span region="Default">Ini akan jadi satu masalah besar.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:09.130"
        end="00:17:11.700"><span region="Default">Naik… naik.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:11.700"
        end="00:17:13.150"><span region="Default">Naik sini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:13.650"
        end="00:17:14.660"><span region="Default">Wah~</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:14.660"
        end="00:17:17.400"><span region="Default">Ia 15 jam perjalanan naik kereta api ke Mushibai.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:18.380"
        end="00:17:19.980"><span region="Default">Tak terasa juga itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:19.980"
        end="00:17:22.599"><span region="Default">Kereta api ini ada gerabak tinjau.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:22.599"
        end="00:17:24.390"><span region="Default">Jom kita pergi teroka!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:24.390"
        end="00:17:25.660"><span region="Default">Saya nak ikut!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:25.660"
        end="00:17:26.880"><span region="Default">Mama Shin-chan,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:26.880"
        end="00:17:30.770"><span region="Default">tolong ambil gambar yang cantik untuk dihantar pada Mama saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:30.770"
        end="00:17:32.170"><span region="Default">Serah ini pada saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:32.170"
        end="00:17:34.790"><span region="Default">Boleh saya bergambar dengan kakak cantik</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:34.790"
        end="00:17:36.190"><span region="Default">dan hantar pada Mama tak?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:36.190"
        end="00:17:37.500"><span region="Default">Tak, terima kasih.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:47.610"
        end="00:17:49.200"><span region="Default">Baik, senyum!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:50.350"
        end="00:17:52.450"><span region="Default">Saya akan hantar ini pada Mama kamu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:52.450"
        end="00:17:55.270"><span region="Default">Mari lihat, pukul berapa di Jepun sekarang ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:55.270"
        end="00:17:56.350"><span region="Default">Tak apalah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:58.560"
        end="00:17:59.690"><span region="Default">Eh? Lajunya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:00.800"
        end="00:18:02.540"><span region="Default">Pasti mereka rasa risau.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:03.550"
        end="00:18:04.890"><span region="Default">Lihat itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:05.970"
        end="00:18:08.610"><span region="Default">Seperti dijangka, ini memang berbeza dari Kasukabe.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:08.610"
        end="00:18:10.590"><span region="Default">India ini memang dinamik, kan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:11.160"
        end="00:18:13.160"><span region="Default">Saya pun nak tengok juga!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:38.530"
        end="00:18:41.670"><span region="Default">Wahai kakak cantik! Saya Shinnosuke Nohara!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:42.070"
        end="00:18:44.550"><span region="Default">Marilah kita keluar makan kari bersama-sama.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:44.550"
        end="00:18:46.450"><span region="Default">Hei, Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:46.450"
        end="00:18:48.880"><span region="Default">Maaf! Maaf! Saya minta maaf!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:48.880"
        end="00:18:50.120"><span region="Default">Eh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:50.120"
        end="00:18:51.750"><span region="Default">Apa yang saya buat tadi?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:52.120"
        end="00:18:54.130"><span region="Default">Hei, awak ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:18:54.130"
        end="00:18:56.530"><span region="Default">Dah sampai India pun, apa yang awak buat ni!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:18.450"
        end="00:19:20.290"><span region="Default">Hei, saya nak ke tandas!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:23.590"
        end="00:19:25.260"><span region="Default">Eh? Saya buat apa tadi?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:38.180"
        end="00:19:39.790"><span region="Default">Alamak, dapat nenek tua!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:40.980"
        end="00:19:43.280"><span region="Default">Main Baba Nuki dengan orang tua-tua pun seronok juga ya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:43.280"
        end="00:19:44.290"><span region="Default">Ya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:44.290"
        end="00:19:46.310"><span region="Default">Awak nak sertai sekali, Encik Uh-huh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:46.310"
        end="00:19:47.450"><span region="Default">Uh-huh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:47.450"
        end="00:19:49.050"><span region="Default">Selamat pulang! Man-shock!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:49.630"
        end="00:19:51.620"><span region="Default">Jangan cakap benda menakutkan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:51.620"
        end="00:19:52.890"><span region="Default">Cakap saya dah balik sajalah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:52.890"
        end="00:19:54.780"><span region="Default">Bagaimana gerabak tinjau itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:54.780"
        end="00:19:55.950"><span region="Default">Ia terbaik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:55.950"
        end="00:19:58.520"><span region="Default">Tuan pengetua ikut sertai kami sekali.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:58.520"
        end="00:19:59.800"><span region="Default">Betul juga itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:19:59.800"
        end="00:20:02.020"><span region="Default">Dah jumpa! Chocobi perisa kari!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:03.680"
        end="00:20:05.460"><span region="Default">Silalah makan, Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:05.460"
        end="00:20:06.660"><span region="Default">Ambil ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:07.280"
        end="00:20:09.310"><span region="Default">Aku lapar-lapar-lapar gila!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:09.310"
        end="00:20:10.770"><span region="Default">Berhenti!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:10.770"
        end="00:20:12.970"><span region="Default">Tiada manisan sebelum makan tengah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:12.970"
        end="00:20:15.450"><span region="Default">Eh? Ibu kedekut!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:15.450"
        end="00:20:17.270"><span region="Default">Biarlah kedekut.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:17.270"
        end="00:20:22.040"><span region="Default">Saya nak makan! Nak makan! Nak makan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:22.040"
        end="00:20:24.010"><span region="Default">- Bo seorang budak yang baik.<br/>- Nak makan! Nak makan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:24.010"
        end="00:20:27.500"><span region="Default">Kita akan singgah stesen dalam 30 minit lagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:27.500"
        end="00:20:30.470"><span region="Default">Jadi, kita akan makan tengah hari di sana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:34.240"
        end="00:20:35.720"><span region="Default">Berdasarkan lakaran muka ini,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:35.720"
        end="00:20:40.100"><span region="Default">cuba jejaki budak yang miliki kertas itu guna litar tertutup</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:40.100"
        end="00:20:42.110"><span region="Default">dan juga pengecaman muka.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:42.110"
        end="00:20:45.200"><span region="Default">Nampaknya mereka naik kereta api menuju Mushibai.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:45.200"
        end="00:20:46.790"><span region="Default">Dan itu kereta apinya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:47.260"
        end="00:20:50.760"><span region="Default">Budak punggung goyang dan budak hingus bergoyang pasti ada dalam sana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:51.230"
        end="00:20:53.790"><span region="Default">Kerja bagus, seperti dijangka dari abang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:53.790"
        end="00:20:57.480"><span region="Default">Apa pun jadi, kita mesti halang kertas tu daripada tercucuk ke hidung sesiapa!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:20:57.480"
        end="00:20:58.530"><span region="Default">Faham!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:33.470"
        end="00:21:35.260"><span region="Default">Tuan Urufu, ini berbahaya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:35.260"
        end="00:21:37.360"><span region="Default">Dalam 2 hari lalu, haiwan liar ini berada—</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:37.360"
        end="00:21:38.750"><span region="Default">Aku cuma nak sapa ia saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:39.210"
        end="00:21:41.380"><span region="Default">Sebab ia berpotensi jadi rakan seiring aku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:42.100"
        end="00:21:45.590"><span region="Default">Rakan seiring yang kuat memang sesuai untuk aku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:46.500"
        end="00:21:49.650"><span region="Default">Cukup ke awak untuk jadi rakan seiring aku?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:51.720"
        end="00:21:53.220"><span region="Default">Kari itu nampak sedap.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:54.090"
        end="00:21:57.480"><span region="Default">Tak sangka ada begitu banyak jenis kari.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:58.730"
        end="00:21:59.850"><span region="Default">Encik Uh-huh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:21:59.850"
        end="00:22:03.410"><span region="Default">Saya nak sesuatu yang kurang pedas untuk budak-budak ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:03.410"
        end="00:22:04.420"><span region="Default">Uh-huh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:05.880"
        end="00:22:08.220"><span region="Default">Hmm… hmm…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:08.220"
        end="00:22:11.310"><span region="Default">Nasi? Naan? Chapati?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:11.310"
        end="00:22:12.520"><span region="Default">Chapati?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:12.520"
        end="00:22:14.850"><span region="Default">Chapati! Chapati! Chapati! Chapati!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:14.850"
        end="00:22:16.390"><span region="Default">Itu Kabaddi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:17.690"
        end="00:22:20.330"><span region="Default">Nampaknya mereka sedang buat Chapati.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:20.820"
        end="00:22:24.450"><span region="Default">Chapati ialah roti yang dibuat dengan uli tepung gandum penuh bersama air.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:24.450"
        end="00:22:25.920"><span region="Default">Kemudian, dibakar atas kuali.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:25.920"
        end="00:22:29.520"><span region="Default">Ia memang makanan kebiasaan bagi orang India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:29.520"
        end="00:22:30.580"><span region="Default">Betul, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:30.580"
        end="00:22:31.590"><span region="Default">Uh-huh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:36.450"
        end="00:22:38.170"><span region="Default">Itu nampak sedap!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:38.170"
        end="00:22:40.140"><span region="Default">Adakah Chapati ini sedap?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:40.920"
        end="00:22:41.940"><span region="Default">Ya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:43.590"
        end="00:22:45.380"><span region="Default">Kalau begitu… aku nak</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:49.070"
        end="00:22:49.850"><span region="Default">Naan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:51.720"
        end="00:22:53.730"><span region="Default">Saya nak nasi!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:53.730"
        end="00:22:54.630"><span region="Default">Saya nak Naan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:54.630"
        end="00:22:55.840"><span region="Default">Saya juga!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:55.840"
        end="00:22:56.620"><span region="Default">Naan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:57.520"
        end="00:22:58.730"><span region="Default">Naan juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:22:58.730"
        end="00:23:01.370"><span region="Default">Saya nak nasi dan juga Naan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:01.370"
        end="00:23:03.580"><span region="Default">Naan. Awak nak juga?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:03.580"
        end="00:23:04.780"><span region="Default">Uh-huh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:04.780"
        end="00:23:06.230"><span region="Default">Saya pula…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:16.920"
        end="00:23:18.250"><span region="Default">Naan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:24.830"
        end="00:23:28.850"><span region="Default">Walaupun begitu, saya masih rasa macam punggung nak pecah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:30.350"
        end="00:23:31.720"><span region="Default">Kari apa itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:31.720"
        end="00:23:33.210"><span region="Default">Ia berbau sangat sedap!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:33.210"
        end="00:23:35.180"><span region="Default">Boleh saya nak rasa sikit?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:35.180"
        end="00:23:37.980"><span region="Default">Saya nak rasa sekali saja…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:23:37.980"
        end="00:23:39.980"><span region="Default">Sekali saja!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:00.570"
        end="00:24:01.800"><span region="Default">Eh? Tak apakah?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:22.220"
        end="00:24:24.950"><span region="Default">Boleh tahan juga rasa kari asli ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:30.850"
        end="00:24:32.620"><span region="Default">Semua ini nampak sedap.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:42.090"
        end="00:24:44.240"><span region="Default">Bo, bagaimana awak buat tadi?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:45.860"
        end="00:24:48.610"><span region="Default">Apa dah jadi pada diri saya ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:50.170"
        end="00:24:51.200"><span region="Default">Naan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:52.090"
        end="00:24:53.130"><span region="Default">Nasi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:53.130"
        end="00:24:54.270"><span region="Default">Naan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:54.270"
        end="00:24:55.390"><span region="Default">Naan dan Nasi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:55.390"
        end="00:24:57.780"><span region="Default">Naan, Naan, Naan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:24:58.730"
        end="00:25:00.280"><span region="Default">Chapati.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:03.580"
        end="00:25:04.720"><span region="Default">Chapati?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:05.180"
        end="00:25:06.540"><span region="Default">Chapati?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:06.540"
        end="00:25:08.000"><span region="Default">Tak apalah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:08.000"
        end="00:25:09.640"><span region="Default">Semua orang dapat tak?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:09.640"
        end="00:25:11.100"><span region="Default">Ya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:11.100"
        end="00:25:12.850"><span region="Default">Shin-chan patutnya dapat Naan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:15.360"
        end="00:25:17.300"><span region="Default">Shin-chan nak Naan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:18.220"
        end="00:25:20.230"><span region="Default">Dia pesan Naan tadi…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:20.230"
        end="00:25:22.670"><span region="Default">Bo, ada apa-apa ke?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:23.500"
        end="00:25:25.330"><span region="Default">Punggung saya lapar sangat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:25.330"
        end="00:25:26.960"><span region="Default">Jemput makan kari masala ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:26.960"
        end="00:25:29.450"><span region="Default">Ia patutnya Naan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:29.450"
        end="00:25:31.100"><span region="Default">Hei!!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:31.100"
        end="00:25:34.020"><span region="Default">Shin-chan nak makan Naan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:34.020"
        end="00:25:35.770"><span region="Default">Patutnya Naan! Naan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:35.770"
        end="00:25:38.290"><span region="Default">Bo! Itu satu tiupan ribut besar!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:40.830"
        end="00:25:41.860"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:43.780"
        end="00:25:44.950"><span region="Default">Hei!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:25:51.570"
        end="00:25:52.990"><span region="Default">Hati-hati!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:00.550"
        end="00:26:02.660"><span region="Default">Haiwan paling menggerunkan dalam dunia!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:02.660"
        end="00:26:05.520"><span region="Default">Itu bejar madu liar!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:13.610"
        end="00:26:14.880"><span region="Default">Ada sesuatu di situ!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:14.880"
        end="00:26:16.080"><span region="Default">Comelnya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:16.470"
        end="00:26:19.470"><span region="Default">Bo! Lihat, kami beli Naan ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:19.470"
        end="00:26:22.680"><span region="Default">Dah ada Naan ini, jadi tolong bawa bertenang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:27.260"
        end="00:26:30.260"><span region="Default">Shin-chan punya Naan! Pulangkan balik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:32.570"
        end="00:26:34.760"><span region="Default">Naan itu untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:34.760"
        end="00:26:36.330"><span region="Default">Lajunya, Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:38.830"
        end="00:26:40.080"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:50.630"
        end="00:26:52.730"><span region="Default">Bertenang, Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:57.640"
        end="00:26:59.770"><span region="Default">Mhm! Uh-huh!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:26:59.780"
        end="00:27:02.400"><span region="Default">Awak tak apa-apa, Encik Uh-huh?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:06.130"
        end="00:27:08.510"><span region="Default">Tunggu kejap, Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:12.840"
        end="00:27:13.930"><span region="Default">Habislah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:14.550"
        end="00:27:16.120"><span region="Default">Kertas itu dah tercucuk!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:17.580"
        end="00:27:20.220"><span region="Default">Baru sebelah sisi! Jangan mengalah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:25.160"
        end="00:27:28.330"><span region="Default">Budak! Keluarkan kertas itu dari hidung awak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:28.680"
        end="00:27:29.760"><span region="Default">Kertas?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:30.480"
        end="00:27:31.660"><span region="Default">Dan kamu ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:32.650"
        end="00:27:37.400"><span region="Default">Kami unit polis siasatan India khas bagi kes misteri yang belum diselesaikan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:37.400"
        end="00:27:41.270"><span region="Default">Nama saya Kabir Katchapapal Pakkapapal Katchapapal Pakkapapal.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:41.270"
        end="00:27:42.590"><span region="Default">Saya Dill, sama dengannya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:42.590"
        end="00:27:45.430"><span region="Default">Kami datang ini untuk ambil balik kertas berbahaya itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:45.900"
        end="00:27:47.820"><span region="Default">Fasihnya Jepun mereka.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:48.250"
        end="00:27:53.970"><span region="Default">Kami ialah askar elit teratas dari 1.45 bilion rakyat India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:53.970"
        end="00:27:55.980"><span region="Default">Saya fasih dalam 12 bahasa,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:55.980"
        end="00:27:58.310"><span region="Default">tapi Dill boleh cakap semua bahasa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:27:58.680"
        end="00:28:00.150"><span region="Default">Semua bahasa?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:00.780"
        end="00:28:04.800"><span region="Default">Jadi, bagaimana nak kata "Saya<br/>boleh jalan guna punggung" dalam India?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:04.800"
        end="00:28:07.400"><span region="Default">"Saya boleh jalan guna punggung."</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:07.400"
        end="00:28:08.730"><span region="Default">Kalau dalam Korea?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:08.730"
        end="00:28:11.040"><span region="Default">"Saya boleh jalan guna punggung."</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:11.450"
        end="00:28:12.890"><span region="Default">Kalau guna dialek Akita?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:12.890"
        end="00:28:14.230"><span region="Default">"Saya boleh jalan guna punggung."</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:16.290"
        end="00:28:17.910"><span region="Default">Apa yang awak cuba nak buat?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:18.490"
        end="00:28:20.320"><span region="Default">Umm… kertas?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:20.720"
        end="00:28:23.790"><span region="Default">Itulah kertas kejahatan yang tercucuk pada hidung budak itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:23.790"
        end="00:28:26.480"><span region="Default">Bila "kertas" itu tercucuck ke hidung,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:26.480"
        end="00:28:29.160"><span region="Default">segala tenaga dalam badan akan terkumpul pada hidung.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:29.160"
        end="00:28:31.280"><span region="Default">Dengan nafas makin berat,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:31.280"
        end="00:28:33.560"><span region="Default">Ia akan hasilkan kuasa yang luar biasa!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:33.560"
        end="00:28:34.890"><span region="Default">Betul itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:34.890"
        end="00:28:38.830"><span region="Default">Lalu, kertas itu akan tunaikan keinginan sesiapa yang tercucuk.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:39.540"
        end="00:28:40.780"><span region="Default">Keinginan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:40.780"
        end="00:28:44.240"><span region="Default">Bila kertas itu masuk sepenuhnya dalam kedua-dua lubang hidung,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:44.240"
        end="00:28:48.970"><span region="Default">budak itu akan mula bertindak kejam agar dapat penuhi keinginannya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:48.970"
        end="00:28:52.220"><span region="Default">Jadi seorang zalim yang buas dan tidak berperikemanusiaan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:52.220"
        end="00:28:54.010"><span region="Default">Kemudian, jadi seorang raja zalim!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:54.010"
        end="00:28:57.680"><span region="Default">Eh?! Bo akan bertukar jadi raja zalim?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:57.680"
        end="00:28:59.780"><span region="Default">Kertas itu baru sebelah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:28:59.780"
        end="00:29:01.840"><span region="Default">Jadi, kuasanya baru separuh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:02.580"
        end="00:29:04.920"><span region="Default">Kita kena tarik kertas itu sekarang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:04.920"
        end="00:29:06.510"><span region="Default">Seperti yang abang suruh!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:21.530"
        end="00:29:23.700"><span region="Default">Naan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:28.200"
        end="00:29:29.930"><span region="Default">Ini Naan untuk awak, Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:29.930"
        end="00:29:31.220"><span region="Default">Terima kasih!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:33.620"
        end="00:29:34.230"><span region="Default">Eh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:34.230"
        end="00:29:35.970"><span region="Default">Cuma ada Naan saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:35.970"
        end="00:29:37.750"><span region="Default">Ia perlukan kari.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:37.750"
        end="00:29:39.380"><span region="Default">Kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:39.380"
        end="00:29:40.910"><span region="Default">Kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:40.910"
        end="00:29:41.730"><span region="Default">Saya perlu kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:41.730"
        end="00:29:42.480"><span region="Default">- Kejap!<br/>- Saya perlu kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:42.480"
        end="00:29:43.480"><span region="Default">Kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:43.480"
        end="00:29:44.760"><span region="Default">- Apa yang jadi?!<br/>- Kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:44.760"
        end="00:29:45.900"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:49.110"
        end="00:29:50.120"><span region="Default">Kuatnya…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:50.920"
        end="00:29:53.050"><span region="Default">Antara calon rakan seiring aku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:53.050"
        end="00:29:57.530"><span region="Default">Dia mampu menewaskan Raja Bejar Madu, yang terkuat antara semua bejar madu ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:29:58.960"
        end="00:30:00.620"><span region="Default">Cepat tangkap dia!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:03.810"
        end="00:30:06.490"><span region="Default">Kari untuk Shin-chan! Kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:06.490"
        end="00:30:09.160"><span region="Default">Kari untuk Shin-chan! Shin-chan tak suka lada hijau.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:09.160"
        end="00:30:10.360"><span region="Default">Shin-chan suka daging.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:10.360"
        end="00:30:11.740"><span region="Default">- Bo!<br/>- Shin-chan suka ikan juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:11.740"
        end="00:30:13.260"><span region="Default">Dan Ayam Tandoori?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:13.260"
        end="00:30:14.980"><span region="Default">Dia suka nasi, suka Naan juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:14.980"
        end="00:30:16.600"><span region="Default">Di situ ada Naan! Ada Naan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:16.600"
        end="00:30:19.940"><span region="Default">Kari untuk Shin-chan! Kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:21.800"
        end="00:30:23.110"><span region="Default">Kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:23.110"
        end="00:30:24.490"><span region="Default">Shin-chan suka daging!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:24.490"
        end="00:30:26.230"><span region="Default">Dia suka ikan, dia suka udang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:26.230"
        end="00:30:28.160"><span region="Default">Dia boleh makan bawang tak?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:28.160"
        end="00:30:31.090"><span region="Default">Untuk Shin-chan, ia tak bagus jika terlalu pedas.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:31.090"
        end="00:30:33.730"><span region="Default">Kari untuk Shin-chan! Kari untuk Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:34.840"
        end="00:30:36.830"><span region="Default">Kejap! Kamu buat apa ini, budak-budak?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:36.830"
        end="00:30:38.600"><span region="Default">Biar kami yang uruskan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:39.930"
        end="00:30:41.970"><span region="Default">Mari tamatkannya di sini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:41.970"
        end="00:30:43.100"><span region="Default">Yeah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:45.780"
        end="00:30:50.060"><span region="Default">Masa untuk kita keluarkan 120% potensi tersembunyi kita.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:50.070"
        end="00:30:52.100"><span region="Default">Itu adalah Kuasa India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:30:57.950"
        end="00:31:00.810"><span region="Default">♪ Mari nyanyikan! Kuasa India! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:00.810"
        end="00:31:03.730"><span region="Default">♪ Boleh kau rasakan dalam diri aku ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:03.730"
        end="00:31:06.600"><span region="Default">♪ Mari menari! Kuasa India! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:06.600"
        end="00:31:09.430"><span region="Default">♪ Aku tahu ia ada! Kuasa yang terpendam ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:09.430"
        end="00:31:12.260"><span region="Default">♪ Terus mara di jalan yang belum diketahui ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:12.260"
        end="00:31:16.790"><span region="Default">♪ Kami Panas! Seperti super kari pedas! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:17.820"
        end="00:31:20.680"><span region="Default">♪ Nyanyian jadikan dirimu kuat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:20.680"
        end="00:31:23.560"><span region="Default">♪ Hentakkan rentak drum ikut degupan jantung ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:23.560"
        end="00:31:26.230"><span region="Default">♪ Tarian jadikan dirimu panas bersemangat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:26.230"
        end="00:31:29.670"><span region="Default">♪ Had? Logik? Chai, chai, chai ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:30.500"
        end="00:31:32.540"><span region="Default">Mereka menyanyi dan menari boleh jadi kuat ke?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:32.540"
        end="00:31:37.980"><span region="Default">♪ Aku tak kisah samosa<br/>hancur ni, itulah laguku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:37.980"
        end="00:31:40.750"><span region="Default">♪ Masala Chai untuk air mata tumpah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:40.750"
        end="00:31:43.620"><span region="Default">♪ Itu Lagu Cinta aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:43.620"
        end="00:31:48.920"><span region="Default">♪ Okay! Kelajuan penuh ke depan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:49.400"
        end="00:31:52.260"><span region="Default">♪ Mari menyanyi! Kuasa India ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:52.260"
        end="00:31:54.980"><span region="Default">♪ Aku boleh rasa dari dalam diri aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:54.980"
        end="00:31:57.980"><span region="Default">♪ Mari menari! Kuasa India ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:31:57.980"
        end="00:32:00.670"><span region="Default">♪ Bangkitkanlah! Kuasa yang tidur! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:00.670"
        end="00:32:03.520"><span region="Default">♪ Terus mara di jalan yang belum diketahui ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:03.520"
        end="00:32:08.190"><span region="Default">♪ Kami panas! Seperti super kari pedas! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:08.730"
        end="00:32:10.780"><span region="Default">- Hebatnya Kuasa India!<br/>♪ Itulah kuasa bersinar di India ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:10.780"
        end="00:32:15.750"><span region="Default">♪ Kuasa India! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:17.290"
        end="00:32:18.400"><span region="Default">Habislah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:18.400"
        end="00:32:19.610"><span region="Default">Kereta api itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:19.610"
        end="00:32:21.170"><span region="Default">Kita kena sampai di Mushibai.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:21.170"
        end="00:32:22.580"><span region="Default">Bo?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:22.580"
        end="00:32:25.380"><span region="Default">Dan bersama-sama buat persembahan di Festival Hiburan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:42.830"
        end="00:32:43.490"><span region="Default">Eh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:47.550"
        end="00:32:48.900"><span region="Default">Tunggu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:53.370"
        end="00:32:54.030"><span region="Default">Sini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:54.980"
        end="00:32:56.230"><span region="Default">Laparnya saya…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:32:58.590"
        end="00:33:00.650"><span region="Default">Jangan kutip itu! Tak boleh!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:00.650"
        end="00:33:01.460"><span region="Default">Apa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:03.730"
        end="00:33:04.500"><span region="Default">Tunggu…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:04.500"
        end="00:33:05.290"><span region="Default">- Mari!<br/>- Tunggu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:05.290"
        end="00:33:06.380"><span region="Default">Tunggu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:21.430"
        end="00:33:24.370"><span region="Default">Entah kenapa… tapi saya nampak hebat, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:28.250"
        end="00:33:30.090"><span region="Default">Saya juga boleh buat ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:31.710"
        end="00:33:33.470"><span region="Default">Apa juga yang dah jadi ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:33.470"
        end="00:33:35.630"><span region="Default">Saya tak pernah lihat Bo begitu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:35.630"
        end="00:33:37.320"><span region="Default">Tunggu, Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:37.320"
        end="00:33:38.960"><span region="Default">Saya boleh buat apa saja!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:42.280"
        end="00:33:43.580"><span region="Default">Ini memang hebat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:33:43.580"
        end="00:33:44.340"><span region="Default">Eh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:01.710"
        end="00:34:04.030"><span region="Default">Bo! Berbahaya itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:04.030"
        end="00:34:05.830"><span region="Default">Cepat tarik kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:06.390"
        end="00:34:07.550"><span region="Default">Kertas?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:07.550"
        end="00:34:11.400"><span region="Default">Tisu yang ada di hidung awak itu yang buat awak jadi pelik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:17.670"
        end="00:34:18.730"><span region="Default">Pelik ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:20.670"
        end="00:34:22.989"><span region="Default">Adakah diri saya ini pelik?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:24.290"
        end="00:34:25.820"><span region="Default">Ini tak pelik.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:26.989"
        end="00:34:28.699"><span region="Default">Langsung tiada yang pelik.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:31.070"
        end="00:34:34.250"><span region="Default">Sebab aku rasa paling terbaik sekarang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:37.949"
        end="00:34:38.770"><span region="Default">Bo…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:38.770"
        end="00:34:40.530"><span region="Default">Budak punggung goyang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:41.060"
        end="00:34:43.150"><span region="Default">Buang beg itu ke sini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:43.830"
        end="00:34:48.670"><span region="Default">Jangan biar budak hingus bergoyang itu rampas sekeping lagi kertas!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:34:53.650"
        end="00:34:56.230"><span region="Default">Ada lagi satu kertas.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:05.500"
        end="00:35:08.600"><span region="Default">Sekeping lagi untuk jadikan ia sempurna.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:09.170"
        end="00:35:11.990"><span region="Default">Saya nak itu! Saya inginkan itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:11.990"
        end="00:35:14.020"><span region="Default">Saya nak! Saya nak! Saya nak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:14.020"
        end="00:35:17.360"><span region="Default">Kertas yang tercucuk pada hidung budak hingus bergoyang itu</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:17.360"
        end="00:35:19.750"><span region="Default">terdesak inginkan cebisan yang lain.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:20.100"
        end="00:35:20.950"><span region="Default">Shiro!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:21.830"
        end="00:35:23.970"><span region="Default">Bo, kenapa dengan awak ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:23.970"
        end="00:35:25.940"><span region="Default">Ini langsung bukan diri awak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:26.560"
        end="00:35:29.410"><span region="Default">Bo biasanya lebih tenang, kan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:29.410"
        end="00:35:30.510"><span region="Default">Betul itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:30.510"
        end="00:35:34.130"><span region="Default">Bo sepatutnya lebih baik hati dan seorang budak baik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:41.640"
        end="00:35:42.800"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:48.900"
        end="00:35:49.960"><span region="Default">Bo…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:51.480"
        end="00:35:54.000"><span region="Default">Apa yang kau tahu pasal diri aku?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:35:57.960"
        end="00:35:59.330"><span region="Default">Bo…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:36:00.360"
        end="00:36:06.890"><span region="Default">Apa yang kau tahu pasal diri aku ini?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:36:16.410"
        end="00:36:18.690"><span region="Default">Aku dah jumpa seseorang yang kuat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:36:21.310"
        end="00:36:22.920"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:36:23.420"
        end="00:36:25.470"><span region="Default">Ayah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:36:32.480"
        end="00:36:33.840"><span region="Default">Eh?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:36:44.250"
        end="00:36:48.420"><span region="Default">Kabir Katchapapal Pakkapapal Katchapapal Pakkapapal!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:36:49.850"
        end="00:36:52.660"><span region="Default">Dill!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:36:52.660"
        end="00:36:54.950"><span region="Default">Masao! Shiro!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:37:02.520"
        end="00:37:06.420"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:37:32.430"
        end="00:37:33.430"><span region="Default">Eh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:37:53.280"
        end="00:37:55.060"><span region="Default">Di… mana ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:37:56.640"
        end="00:37:59.780"><span region="Default">Ayah! Ibu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:12.830"
        end="00:38:16.320"><span region="Default">Ini adalah Mushibai, Hagashimir.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:17.260"
        end="00:38:19.750"><span region="Default">Lokasi Festival Hiburan itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:21.290"
        end="00:38:22.370"><span region="Default">Hei, Kiub.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:22.900"
        end="00:38:23.600"><span region="Default">Ya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:24.200"
        end="00:38:26.340"><span region="Default">Tukar kereta aku jadi pemanduan automatik.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:26.850"
        end="00:38:28.200"><span region="Default">Menurut perintah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:36.020"
        end="00:38:38.030"><span region="Default">Mari datang ke istanaku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:38.370"
        end="00:38:39.380"><span region="Default">Mari naik.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:39.380"
        end="00:38:41.600"><span region="Default">Awak dijemput ke istanaku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:41.600"
        end="00:38:42.940"><span region="Default">Sila naik ke dalam kereta.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:42.940"
        end="00:38:44.410"><span region="Default">Janganlah rasa segan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:44.410"
        end="00:38:47.150"><span region="Default">Sebab kau itu akan jadi rakan seiring aku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:48.150"
        end="00:38:49.260"><span region="Default">Betul, tak?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:51.650"
        end="00:38:55.220"><span region="Default">Hei, apa yang awak cuba nak buat?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:56.920"
        end="00:38:57.980"><span region="Default">Sayang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:38:59.290"
        end="00:39:01.570"><span region="Default">Bo, jangan dekat dengan dia!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:02.540"
        end="00:39:04.250"><span region="Default">Lepaskan saya, tak guna!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:04.250"
        end="00:39:08.310"><span region="Default">Jangan risau, papa dan mama Shin-chan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:08.310"
        end="00:39:09.420"><span region="Default">Huh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:10.960"
        end="00:39:12.250"><span region="Default">Sekarang, aku…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:12.780"
        end="00:39:16.230"><span region="Default">tak perlukan sesiapa untuk lindungi diri aku ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:17.430"
        end="00:39:18.550"><span region="Default">Bo?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:19.030"
        end="00:39:21.230"><span region="Default">Baiklah! Mari kita pergi, kawanku!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:21.230"
        end="00:39:23.210"><span region="Default">Manakala semua orang boleh di belakang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:26.440"
        end="00:39:29.100"><span region="Default">Kejap! Awak nak buat apa pada budak-budak ini?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:32.480"
        end="00:39:33.490"><span region="Default">Awak nak buat apa?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:33.490"
        end="00:39:34.980"><span region="Default">- Layanan apakah ini?!<br/>- Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:34.980"
        end="00:39:36.030"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:36.450"
        end="00:39:37.660"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:37.660"
        end="00:39:40.670"><span region="Default">Kita kena segera cari Shinnosuke dan Masao!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:40.670"
        end="00:39:42.290"><span region="Default">Serah saja pada aku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:42.290"
        end="00:39:44.160"><span region="Default">Aku akan siapkan dengan sempurna.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:44.160"
        end="00:39:45.400"><span region="Default">Siapkan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:45.680"
        end="00:39:47.480"><span region="Default">Kan ini Festival Hiburan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:47.480"
        end="00:39:51.170"><span region="Default">Kita datang ke sini untuk buat persembahan di sana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:51.170"
        end="00:39:55.270"><span region="Default">Kami rancang untuk buat persembahan di Festival Hiburan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:55.270"
        end="00:39:57.110"><span region="Default">Macam itukah?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:39:57.110"
        end="00:40:01.650"><span region="Default">Baiklah demi kawanku, Bo, aku akan beli seluruh festival itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:01.650"
        end="00:40:03.250"><span region="Default">Beli seluruh festival?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:03.250"
        end="00:40:04.810"><span region="Default">Itu tak mungkin berlaku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:08.530"
        end="00:40:12.600"><span region="Default">Ini kiub hebat yang aku bangunkan dengan 1 trilion yen.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:12.600"
        end="00:40:17.980"><span region="Default">Ia secara langsung berhubung dengan talian global melalui satelit.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:17.980"
        end="00:40:19.500"><span region="Default">Dan boleh buat apa saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:19.500"
        end="00:40:20.770"><span region="Default">(Bayar)</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:20.770"
        end="00:40:22.900"><span region="Default">Sekarang, festival itu milik kita.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:23.470"
        end="00:40:24.780"><span region="Default">Buatlah apa yang kau nak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:24.790"
        end="00:40:29.040"><span region="Default">"Urufu &amp; Bo mempersembahkan Festival Hiburan!"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:30.350"
        end="00:40:31.690"><span region="Default">Tak perlu terima kasih.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:31.690"
        end="00:40:34.330"><span region="Default">Aku ini adalah rakan seiring Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:34.860"
        end="00:40:35.920"><span region="Default">Betul tak?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:36.670"
        end="00:40:38.880"><span region="Default">Hei! Jangan cuba dekati Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:38.880"
        end="00:40:40.490"><span region="Default">Siapa juga awak ini?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:42.050"
        end="00:40:43.280"><span region="Default">Wahai Kiub!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:43.280"
        end="00:40:44.000"><span region="Default">Ya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:44.000"
        end="00:40:46.510"><span region="Default">Mainkan muzik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:47.100"
        end="00:40:47.900"><span region="Default">♪ Yeah! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:49.480"
        end="00:40:51.280"><span region="Default">♪ Lelaki kaya yang hebat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:51.280"
        end="00:40:52.320"><span region="Default">♪ Yeah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:53.370"
        end="00:40:54.960"><span region="Default">♪ Semua orang sukakan diri aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:54.960"
        end="00:40:59.530"><span region="Default">♪ Yeah, Ho-Ho! Bergaya! Lelaki kaya! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:40:59.530"
        end="00:41:01.690"><span region="Default">♪ Yeah, bergaya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:01.690"
        end="00:41:03.290"><span region="Default">Biar aku cerita tentang diriku</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:03.290"
        end="00:41:07.970"><span region="Default">♪ Tangisan pertamaku bergema di Sungai Ganges, Aku adalah Urufu Si Sempurna ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:07.970"
        end="00:41:10.280"><span region="Default">♪ Lelaki terbaik dalam India ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:10.280"
        end="00:41:12.120"><span region="Default">♪ Bergaya! Lelaki kaya! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:12.120"
        end="00:41:14.220"><span region="Default">♪ Rambut aku setinggi Kangchenjunga ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:14.220"
        end="00:41:16.230"><span region="Default">♪ Satu trilion yen itu sedikit bagi aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:16.230"
        end="00:41:20.500"><span region="Default">♪ Duit boleh beli bahagia, kesihatan dan tidur lena ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:20.510"
        end="00:41:23.390"><span region="Default">♪ Semua orang sukakan diri aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:23.780"
        end="00:41:27.300"><span region="Default">♪ Yeah! Sempurna satu-satunya yang aku ingin ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:28.030"
        end="00:41:32.640"><span region="Default">♪ Yeah! Mengembara bersama rakan seiring yang kuat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:32.960"
        end="00:41:35.850"><span region="Default">♪ Setelah mengembara ke merata tempat, akhirnya aku temui ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:35.850"
        end="00:41:37.160"><span region="Default">♪ Encik Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:37.160"
        end="00:41:39.210"><span region="Default">Beritahu saja dan aku akan beri semuanya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:39.220"
        end="00:41:42.780"><span region="Default">♪ Aku dah tak boleh hidup tanpa kau ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:42.780"
        end="00:41:45.030"><span region="Default">♪ Kau pun rasa begitu kan? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:45.030"
        end="00:41:47.530"><span region="Default">♪ Itulah rakan seiring aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:47.540"
        end="00:41:52.830"><span region="Default">♪ Selagi kau ada, musim sejuk pun jadi hangat sekali ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:52.830"
        end="00:41:55.890"><span region="Default">♪ Itu satu kehangatan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:41:55.890"
        end="00:42:01.160"><span region="Default">♪ Kau selalu curi hatiku, ubah jadi kari ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:01.160"
        end="00:42:04.190"><span region="Default">♪ Itu satu pencurian ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:05.260"
        end="00:42:08.730"><span region="Default">Kenapa dengan dia itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:08.730"
        end="00:42:11.900"><span region="Default">Jangan tinggalkan saya sendiri… Dill…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:11.900"
        end="00:42:13.830"><span region="Default">Awak ini polis, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:13.830"
        end="00:42:17.640"><span region="Default">Menyanyilah seperti sebelum ini dan buat sesuatu dengan Kuasa India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:17.650"
        end="00:42:19.920"><span region="Default">Mari menyanyi…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:20.800"
        end="00:42:24.470"><span region="Default">Kuasa India…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:24.470"
        end="00:42:25.520"><span region="Default">Gelapnya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:26.410"
        end="00:42:29.200"><span region="Default">Ada apa juga dengan kertas itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:29.200"
        end="00:42:31.990"><span region="Default">Awak kata ia boleh tunaikan permintaan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:31.990"
        end="00:42:33.740"><span region="Default">Saya teringin nak makan…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:33.740"
        end="00:42:35.370"><span region="Default">Saya nak itu…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:35.380"
        end="00:42:39.120"><span region="Default">Keinginan manusia ini tiada had seperti sedalam lautan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:40.060"
        end="00:42:46.500"><span region="Default">Kertas itu akan beri kuasa pada penggunanya agar boleh tunaikan keinginan mereka.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:46.500"
        end="00:42:48.810"><span region="Default">Kuasa untuk tunaikan keinginan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:49.980"
        end="00:42:51.080"><span region="Default">Sejak dari dulu lagi,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:51.080"
        end="00:42:53.610"><span region="Default">ada khabar angin mengatakan bahawa</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:42:53.610"
        end="00:42:59.570"><span region="Default">raja zalim mungkin dipengaruhi oleh kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:00.710"
        end="00:43:04.290"><span region="Default">Kali terakhir kewujudan kertas itu disahkan</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:04.290"
        end="00:43:06.370"><span region="Default">adalah 35 tahun lalu di India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:06.370"
        end="00:43:10.720"><span region="Default">Datang seekor gajah India musnahkan kampung dengan sebelah gading saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:11.050"
        end="00:43:12.480"><span region="Default">Gajah India?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:12.780"
        end="00:43:16.550"><span region="Default">Ia sebuah kampung indah dengan tanaman pokok pisang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:18.270"
        end="00:43:19.470"><span region="Default">Memang betul!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:19.480"
        end="00:43:22.180"><span region="Default">Ada kertas tercucuk di belalai gajah itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:23.180"
        end="00:43:24.420"><span region="Default">Mungkin…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:24.420"
        end="00:43:30.990"><span region="Default">Keinginan gajah itu nak makan pisang membuatnya ia hancurkan kampung tersebut.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:30.990"
        end="00:43:33.280"><span region="Default">Apa yang berlaku pada Bo-chan nanti?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:33.760"
        end="00:43:38.260"><span region="Default">Jika kedua-dua kertas itu masuk sepenuhnya dalam lubang hidung manusia,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:38.260"
        end="00:43:42.150"><span region="Default">ia akan bersatu dengannya dan membuat orang itu menjadi zalim.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:45.620"
        end="00:43:49.140"><span region="Default">♪ Aku dah tak boleh hidup tanpa kau ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:49.140"
        end="00:43:51.410"><span region="Default">♪ Adakah kau juga sama? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:51.410"
        end="00:43:53.960"><span region="Default">♪ Itulah rakan seiring aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:53.960"
        end="00:43:59.210"><span region="Default">♪ Sedangkan kau mampu hentikan arus kesedihan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:43:59.220"
        end="00:44:02.300"><span region="Default">♪ Itu adalah benteng ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:02.310"
        end="00:44:03.710"><span region="Default">♪ Kau ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:03.710"
        end="00:44:07.480"><span region="Default">- Kenapa dengan dia itu? ♪ bagaikan ketulan emas bersinar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:07.870"
        end="00:44:09.050"><span region="Default">Misae?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:09.050"
        end="00:44:11.670"><span region="Default">Masa saya nampak kertas tu dulu,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:11.680"
        end="00:44:14.850"><span region="Default">saya terasa sangat menginginkannya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:14.850"
        end="00:44:16.820"><span region="Default">Tapi sekarang langsung tak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:17.300"
        end="00:44:20.620"><span region="Default">Sebab kertas itu dah dapat budak itu,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:20.620"
        end="00:44:24.870"><span region="Default">jadi ia tak perlu nak hasut sesiapa lagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:25.290"
        end="00:44:28.780"><span region="Default">Cuma sekarang dia perlukan kepingan yang lain</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:28.780"
        end="00:44:34.300"><span region="Default">dari budak punggung goyang itu untuk menjadi raja zalim.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:34.310"
        end="00:44:36.490"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke ada kertas yang lain?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:36.490"
        end="00:44:38.950"><span region="Default">Dua kepingan yang ingin menjadi satu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:39.370"
        end="00:44:41.630"><span region="Default">Disebabkan hal ini dah terjadi,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:41.630"
        end="00:44:44.190"><span region="Default">bagi mengelakkan kezaliman itu lahir…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:44.190"
        end="00:44:49.590"><span region="Default">kita kena bawa lari budak punggung goyang itu jauh dari sini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:49.600"
        end="00:44:52.680"><span region="Default">Dia bukan sekadar budak punggung goyang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:52.680"
        end="00:44:54.280"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke itu…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:54.280"
        end="00:44:59.110"><span region="Default">adalah budak comel, tembam, dan kesayangan saya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:59.110"
        end="00:45:01.880"><span region="Default">Itulah Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:01.880"
        end="00:45:07.160"><span region="Default">♪ Jika kau nak lihat hati aku, aku akan tunjukkan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:07.160"
        end="00:45:10.200"><span region="Default">♪ Itulah pembedahan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:10.210"
        end="00:45:15.900"><span region="Default">♪ Suara lembut kau menyapu lembut telinga aku ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:15.900"
        end="00:45:17.910"><span region="Default">♪ Itu adalah putik kapas ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:59.760"
        end="00:46:00.930"><span region="Default">"Awak rasa lapar ke?"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:01.580"
        end="00:46:02.530"><span region="Default">"Kan?"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:02.760"
        end="00:46:05.760"><span region="Default">Saya seorang budak…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:12.980"
        end="00:46:14.320"><span region="Default">"Hello."</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:14.320"
        end="00:46:16.830"><span region="Default">"Saya nak tanya, semalam anak saya…"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:16.830"
        end="00:46:19.380"><span region="Default">"balik ke rumah dan bawa teman wanitanya…"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:20.880"
        end="00:46:21.740"><span region="Default">Yo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:32.780"
        end="00:46:33.900"><span region="Default">Hei!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:33.900"
        end="00:46:35.260"><span region="Default">Bye-bye!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:41.410"
        end="00:46:42.730"><span region="Default">Gajah…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:43.940"
        end="00:46:45.470"><span region="Default">Gajah…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:49.170"
        end="00:46:51.810"><span region="Default">Gajah! Gajah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:51.810"
        end="00:46:54.910"><span region="Default">Aku ni budak popular!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:56.800"
        end="00:46:58.280"><span region="Default">♪ 1, 2, 3 ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:09.750"
        end="00:47:14.550"><span region="Default">♪ Panik, panik, semua orang berasa panik ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:15.580"
        end="00:47:18.890"><span region="Default">♪ Aku ini sangat hebat, begitu genius ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:18.890"
        end="00:47:20.550"><span region="Default">♪ Oh, oh, oh, oh ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:21.430"
        end="00:47:26.440"><span region="Default">♪ Kuat, kuat, kuat, kelajuan penuh Misae ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:26.920"
        end="00:47:30.820"><span region="Default">♪ Ia satu hari yang bebal, tapi saya baik-baik saja ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:30.820"
        end="00:47:31.980"><span region="Default">Namaste!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:32.700"
        end="00:47:34.980"><span region="Default">♪ Berkait pasal mengurat perempuan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:35.670"
        end="00:47:37.790"><span region="Default">♪ Serahkan saja pada saya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:38.430"
        end="00:47:40.870"><span region="Default">♪ Dalam 3 ataupun 4 ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:41.550"
        end="00:47:43.960"><span region="Default">♪ Itu kunci untuk berjaya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:44.840"
        end="00:47:47.780"><span region="Default">♪ Mari, sayang! Mari, sayang!♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:47.790"
        end="00:47:49.980"><span region="Default">♪ Boleh awak makan bawang?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:50.550"
        end="00:47:53.620"><span region="Default">♪ Saya jadi malu jika awak terus merenung saya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:53.620"
        end="00:47:55.970"><span region="Default">♪ Gajah, Gajah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:55.970"
        end="00:47:58.300"><span region="Default">♪ Aku ni budak popular ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:58.300"
        end="00:47:59.490"><span region="Default">Namaste!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:59.490"
        end="00:48:04.610"><span region="Default">♪ Panik, panik, semua orang berasa panik ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:05.230"
        end="00:48:08.490"><span region="Default">♪ Aku ini sangat hebat, begitu genius ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:08.490"
        end="00:48:12.840"><span region="Default">♪ Saya nantikannya di masa akan datang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:18.650"
        end="00:48:20.190"><span region="Default">♪ Namaste! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:22.280"
        end="00:48:23.600"><span region="Default">♪ Yey, yey ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:25.050"
        end="00:48:26.570"><span region="Default">♪ Yey! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:28.690"
        end="00:48:31.650"><span region="Default">♪ Mari, sayang! Mari, sayang! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:31.650"
        end="00:48:33.840"><span region="Default">♪ Boleh awak makan bawang? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:34.390"
        end="00:48:37.480"><span region="Default">♪ Saya jadi malu jika awak terus merenung saya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:37.480"
        end="00:48:39.880"><span region="Default">♪ Gajah, Gajah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:39.880"
        end="00:48:42.230"><span region="Default">♪ Aku ni budak popular ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:42.240"
        end="00:48:43.340"><span region="Default">Namaste!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:43.340"
        end="00:48:48.130"><span region="Default">♪ Panik, panik, semua orang berasa panik ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:49.160"
        end="00:48:52.400"><span region="Default">♪ Aku ini sangat hebat, begitu genius ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:52.400"
        end="00:48:56.890"><span region="Default">♪ Saya nantikannya di masa akan datang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:57.150"
        end="00:48:58.610"><span region="Default">Hei, kakak cantik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:58.620"
        end="00:48:59.770"><span region="Default">Awak suka lada hijau?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:59.770"
        end="00:49:01.400"><span region="Default">Suka makan lobak?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:01.400"
        end="00:49:03.510"><span region="Default">Awak letak bawang hijau dalam natto?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:03.510"
        end="00:49:06.510"><span region="Default">Ataupun kita patut buat ini…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:15.660"
        end="00:49:19.420"><span region="Default">Saya harap… kamu semua berasa gembira!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:19.420"
        end="00:49:21.470"><span region="Default">Itu memang bagus, Ariana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:21.470"
        end="00:49:23.360"><span region="Default">Sangat bagus.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:23.360"
        end="00:49:27.480"><span region="Default">Pastikan awak hiburkan semua orang di festival dengan senyuman itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:27.480"
        end="00:49:29.430"><span region="Default">Baik! Saya akan buat yang terbaik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:29.890"
        end="00:49:31.690"><span region="Default">Ariana sedang berlatih.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:31.700"
        end="00:49:33.010"><span region="Default">Eh? Mari pergi lihat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:33.010"
        end="00:49:33.790"><span region="Default">Ya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:33.790"
        end="00:49:35.300"><span region="Default">Itu Ariana!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:35.880"
        end="00:49:36.780"><span region="Default">Ariana!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:36.780"
        end="00:49:39.200"><span region="Default">Ariana, kami semua menyokong awak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:39.900"
        end="00:49:42.080"><span region="Default">Ia hampir tiba, Ariana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:42.090"
        end="00:49:45.490"><span region="Default">Ayah dan ibu di sini selalu menyokong awak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:45.490"
        end="00:49:47.420"><span region="Default">Buat yang terbaik dan selalu tersenyum.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:47.420"
        end="00:49:48.650"><span region="Default">Saya tahu juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:48.660"
        end="00:49:51.230"><span region="Default">Saya dah nak gerak ini, jumpa nanti.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:57.290"
        end="00:49:58.810"><span region="Default">Saya kena selalu tersenyum.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:59.320"
        end="00:50:02.580"><span region="Default">Tiada orang nak lihat saya murung.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:08.940"
        end="00:50:16.060"><span region="Default">♪ Aku tersenyum demi orang lain ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:17.660"
        end="00:50:22.110"><span region="Default">♪ Menjadi diri indahku, yang terpantul di mata semua orang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:23.730"
        end="00:50:31.080"><span region="Default">♪ Aku nak terus bersinar, tapi aku rasa sedikit kecewa ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:31.090"
        end="00:50:35.430"><span region="Default">♪ Aku tak nak diri aku dibenci ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:35.430"
        end="00:50:39.720"><span region="Default">♪ Aku cuma tak nak berseorangan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:39.720"
        end="00:50:41.720"><span region="Default">♪ Aku selalu jadi budak baik ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:41.720"
        end="00:50:46.080"><span region="Default">♪ Kadang-kala aku pun tak tahu ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:56.440"
        end="00:50:57.480"><span region="Default">Apa pula itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:57.480"
        end="00:50:58.250"><span region="Default">Sekali lagi!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:02.070"
        end="00:51:03.090"><span region="Default">Bagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:03.440"
        end="00:51:04.470"><span region="Default">Apa itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:04.470"
        end="00:51:07.260"><span region="Default">Jika awak rasa murung, makanlah benda manis,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:07.260"
        end="00:51:09.750"><span region="Default">dan manjakan diri habis-habisan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:09.750"
        end="00:51:11.400"><span region="Default">Itu yang ibu aku selalu kata.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:11.400"
        end="00:51:14.020"><span region="Default">Saya bukannya rasa murung pun.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:14.580"
        end="00:51:16.220"><span region="Default">Awak boleh faham aku?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:16.220"
        end="00:51:18.560"><span region="Default">Aku dah boleh cakap bahasa India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:18.560"
        end="00:51:20.310"><span region="Default">Aku memang genius!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:20.310"
        end="00:51:22.770"><span region="Default">Sebab saya cakap bahasa Jepun.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:22.770"
        end="00:51:25.660"><span region="Default">Saya ini peminat anime jadi saya belajar bahasa Jepun.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:26.040"
        end="00:51:28.650"><span region="Default">Bersinarlah! Perasaan suka ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:28.650"
        end="00:51:32.000"><span region="Default">Persahabatan mendebarkan! Cinta! Harga diri!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:32.010"
        end="00:51:34.260"><span region="Default">Goyang Goyang Penjaga Punggung!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:34.960"
        end="00:51:36.780"><span region="Default">Awak pun tahu pasal itu juga?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:36.790"
        end="00:51:38.890"><span region="Default">Saya tontonnya dengan Himawari.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:41.820"
        end="00:51:45.550"><span region="Default">Seorang gadis biasa yang tempuhi cabaran bersama rakannya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:45.550"
        end="00:51:49.720"><span region="Default">Demi kebahagiaannya dan juga kebahagiaan orang lain.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:51.300"
        end="00:51:54.880"><span region="Default">Goyang Goyang Penjaga Punggung!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:55.490"
        end="00:51:56.910"><span region="Default">Begitu bergaya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:56.910"
        end="00:51:59.220"><span region="Default">Aku, Penjaga Punggun Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:59.220"
        end="00:52:01.830"><span region="Default">Aku, Penjaga Punggun Ariana!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:04.050"
        end="00:52:06.230"><span region="Default">Jadi, apa yang awak buat di sini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:06.230"
        end="00:52:09.460"><span region="Default">Saya sedang mencari Bo dan lain ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:10.540"
        end="00:52:11.690"><span region="Default">Bo?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:14.730"
        end="00:52:16.230"><span region="Default">Ini tak bagus…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:16.230"
        end="00:52:18.380"><span region="Default">Dengan sesat di negara India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:18.380"
        end="00:52:22.310"><span region="Default">Saya tak faham bahasa mereka.<br/>Dan saya langsung tiada duit.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:22.670"
        end="00:52:24.430"><span region="Default">Ia akan berakhir di sini…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:30.340"
        end="00:52:33.470"><span region="Default">Sedangkan saya tak tahu nak buat apa pada diri saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:33.470"
        end="00:52:35.900"><span region="Default">Ini pula nak jaga seekor anjing lagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:51.880"
        end="00:53:54.810"><span region="Default">Saya akan ikut awak ke mana saja, Sifu Shiro!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:13.980"
        end="00:54:17.900"><span region="Default">Bo, mana Papa dan Mama Shin-chan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:18.310"
        end="00:54:19.750"><span region="Default">Tak perlu risau.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:38.010"
        end="00:54:42.480"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke! Masao! Shiro!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:44.110"
        end="00:54:46.500"><span region="Default">Harap kamu semua tak apa-apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:47.080"
        end="00:54:48.170"><span region="Default">Dill…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:49.290"
        end="00:54:52.400"><span region="Default">Orang dewasa diberi tugas untuk membuat kari.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:58.020"
        end="00:55:00.040"><span region="Default">Apa yang awak buat itu, Bo?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:01.940"
        end="00:55:04.540"><span region="Default">Mempersiapkan festival ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:05.190"
        end="00:55:08.360"><span region="Default">Buat kostum dan lagu aku!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:11.580"
        end="00:55:14.650"><span region="Default">Aku dah sediakannya semua dengan duit aku sendiri.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:14.650"
        end="00:55:17.870"><span region="Default">Kau tak perlu risau. Semua ini murah saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:17.870"
        end="00:55:21.360"><span region="Default">Semuanya demi rakan seiring aku, Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:22.260"
        end="00:55:23.420"><span region="Default">Betul tak?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:25.700"
        end="00:55:26.860"><span region="Default">Betul tak?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:31.020"
        end="00:55:35.040"><span region="Default">Bo. Hei, mengenai kertas di hidung awak itu…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:35.040"
        end="00:55:37.140"><span region="Default">Mungkin tiba masa untuk buangnya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:37.150"
        end="00:55:39.000"><span region="Default">Jika ia tercucuk terus, mungkin bahaya—</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:39.010"
        end="00:55:40.620"><span region="Default">Ia bukannya berbahaya pun.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:40.630"
        end="00:55:43.270"><span region="Default">Sebab aku dalam keadan terbaik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:43.270"
        end="00:55:47.330"><span region="Default">Bo! Awak tak rasa risau pada Shin-chan dan Masao-kun?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:50.540"
        end="00:55:52.870"><span region="Default">(Pengecaman muka - Mencari sekarang)</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:52.880"
        end="00:55:54.590"><span region="Default">(Sepadan! 99.9%)</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:54.700"
        end="00:55:55.920"><span region="Default">- Shin-chan!<br/>- Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:55:56.180"
        end="00:55:57.490"><span region="Default">Jumpa pun.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:01.260"
        end="00:56:03.160"><span region="Default">Dia nampak baik-baik saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:03.160"
        end="00:56:05.690"><span region="Default">Syukurlah jika Shinnosuke tak apa-apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:05.690"
        end="00:56:07.130"><span region="Default">Apalah, Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:07.140"
        end="00:56:10.370"><span region="Default">Rupanya awak cuba mencari Shin-chan dan lain.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:10.370"
        end="00:56:12.480"><span region="Default">Patut cakap awal-awal.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:14.950"
        end="00:56:17.020"><span region="Default">Dah jumpa… kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:20.300"
        end="00:56:22.960"><span region="Default">Kau tunggu di situ, Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:36.590"
        end="00:56:40.360"><span region="Default">Dalam kata lain, budak Bo ini masukkan sekepingan kertas ke hidungnya</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:40.360"
        end="00:56:44.810"><span region="Default">lalu dia peroleh satu kuasa kuat yang boleh tunaikan apa saja keinginannya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:45.290"
        end="00:56:47.810"><span region="Default">Mungkin… macam itulah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:54.200"
        end="00:56:59.110"><span region="Default">Jika awak ada kuasa untuk tunaikan apa saja yang awak inginkan,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:56:59.120"
        end="00:57:00.830"><span region="Default">awak teringin nak apa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:02.780"
        end="00:57:03.940"><span region="Default">Saya…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:05.080"
        end="00:57:06.740"><span region="Default">…baring saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:06.740"
        end="00:57:09.190"><span region="Default">Maksud saya, bermalas-malasan saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:09.190"
        end="00:57:10.690"><span region="Default">Tiada buat apa-apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:10.990"
        end="00:57:12.270"><span region="Default">Apa pula itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:13.180"
        end="00:57:15.770"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke, awak tak perlu pun kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:17.870"
        end="00:57:18.880"><span region="Default">Benda apa itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:28.620"
        end="00:57:29.720"><span region="Default">Apa benda itu?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:30.960"
        end="00:57:32.460"><span region="Default">Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:32.460"
        end="00:57:33.580"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:33.580"
        end="00:57:35.270"><span region="Default">Festival itu dah nak bermula.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:36.230"
        end="00:57:37.680"><span region="Default">Saya memang nak ke sana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:37.680"
        end="00:57:39.130"><span region="Default">Jangan risau.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:39.140"
        end="00:57:42.830"><span region="Default">Aku akan bawa kau ke sini dengan selamat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:43.380"
        end="00:57:46.420"><span region="Default">Jadi… kau masih ada kertas itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:47.540"
        end="00:57:49.840"><span region="Default">Kau masih ada Hanagelina Jolie itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:49.840"
        end="00:57:50.820"><span region="Default">Apa dah jadi ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:50.820"
        end="00:57:53.840"><span region="Default">Bo, awak dalam situ ke?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:53.840"
        end="00:57:55.370"><span region="Default">Aku bukan dalam situ.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:55.380"
        end="00:57:57.570"><span region="Default">Pastikan ada "kertas" itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:57.570"
        end="00:57:59.190"><span region="Default">"Cengkerik. (Minminzemi)"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:57:59.190"
        end="00:58:00.390"><span region="Default">"Tasik. (Mizuumi)"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:00.390"
        end="00:58:01.700"><span region="Default">"Rambut tocang. (Mitsuami)"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:01.700"
        end="00:58:02.570"><span region="Default">"Telinga. (Mimi)"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:02.570"
        end="00:58:03.820"><span region="Default">"Telinga kanan. (Migimimi)"</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:03.820"
        end="00:58:06.010"><span region="Default">Mi… mi… ah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:06.010"
        end="00:58:08.270"><span region="Default">Ini bukan masa nak bermain!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:08.280"
        end="00:58:11.610"><span region="Default">I… India memang terbaik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:12.970"
        end="00:58:14.310"><span region="Default">Kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:18.760"
        end="00:58:21.650"><span region="Default">Kau ada kertas itu, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:21.650"
        end="00:58:23.610"><span region="Default">Kau ada kata sebelum ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:23.610"
        end="00:58:26.230"><span region="Default">Aku boleh guna bila-bila masa saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:26.850"
        end="00:58:28.890"><span region="Default">Sekarang masanya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:28.900"
        end="00:58:31.440"><span region="Default">Aku nak kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:31.440"
        end="00:58:32.840"><span region="Default">Nak kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:32.840"
        end="00:58:34.530"><span region="Default">Nak kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:34.530"
        end="00:58:36.040"><span region="Default">Nak kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:36.040"
        end="00:58:37.190"><span region="Default">Bo?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:38.550"
        end="00:58:41.990"><span region="Default">Shin-chan, cepat beri aku kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:43.200"
        end="00:58:45.180"><span region="Default">Lari, Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:54.420"
        end="00:58:55.560"><span region="Default">Kazama?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:57.380"
        end="00:58:59.970"><span region="Default">Lari cepat, Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:58:59.970"
        end="00:59:02.480"><span region="Default">Jangan beri kertas itu pada Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:59:02.480"
        end="00:59:04.790"><span region="Default">Tolong buang benda itu jauh-jauh!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:59:06.330"
        end="00:59:08.870"><span region="Default">Hentikannya! Lepaskan saya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:59:08.870"
        end="00:59:10.810"><span region="Default">Kazama!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:59:14.870"
        end="00:59:16.410"><span region="Default">Bahaya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:59:17.740"
        end="00:59:18.990"><span region="Default">Jangan nak mengacau!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:59:21.300"
        end="00:59:22.740"><span region="Default">Ariana!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:03.370"
        end="01:00:05.090"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke! Belakang awak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:06.110"
        end="01:00:07.410"><span region="Default">Goyang-goyang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:11.120"
        end="01:00:12.320"><span region="Default">Berjaya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:13.010"
        end="01:00:15.550"><span region="Default">Kita nampak sama seperti Penjaga Punggung!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:15.560"
        end="01:00:16.790"><span region="Default">Betul itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:16.790"
        end="01:00:19.250"><span region="Default">Goyang-goyang Penjaga Punggung.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:19.260"
        end="01:00:21.130"><span region="Default">Bukankah itu Ariana?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:21.460"
        end="01:00:22.530"><span region="Default">Ariana?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:40.470"
        end="01:00:42.810"><span region="Default">Ariana!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:52.480"
        end="01:00:54.830"><span region="Default">- Lepaskan saya!<br/>- Bahagian Shin-chan, selesai.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:54.830"
        end="01:00:57.480"><span region="Default">- Lepaskan dia!<br/>- Cuma tinggal Masao.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:57.480"
        end="01:00:59.280"><span region="Default">Bagaimana dengan mereka?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:00:59.290"
        end="01:01:01.550"><span region="Default">- Lepaskan!<br/>- Nak suruh mereka potong bawang?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:01.860"
        end="01:01:03.260"><span region="Default">Lepaskan dia.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:03.270"
        end="01:01:05.110"><span region="Default">Lepaskan aku!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:08.840"
        end="01:01:10.690"><span region="Default">Awak tak apa-apa, Kazama?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:10.690"
        end="01:01:11.480"><span region="Default">Ya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:16.710"
        end="01:01:18.870"><span region="Default">Tolonglah, Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:18.880"
        end="01:01:21.290"><span region="Default">Keluarkan kertas itu dari hidung awak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:21.290"
        end="01:01:24.430"><span region="Default">Sebab itu, awak jadi pelik begini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:25.240"
        end="01:01:26.810"><span region="Default">Tiada apa yang pelik pun.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:28.760"
        end="01:01:30.210"><span region="Default">Kau tak tahu ke?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:31.230"
        end="01:01:34.690"><span region="Default">Ini adalah diri aku… yang sebenar.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:36.230"
        end="01:01:37.430"><span region="Default">Nene!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:37.430"
        end="01:01:40.540"><span region="Default">Kamu dua, tukar pakaian pentas kamu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:41.140"
        end="01:01:43.240"><span region="Default">Festival akan bermula tak lama lagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:48.110"
        end="01:01:49.400"><span region="Default">Alahai…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:49.400"
        end="01:01:50.610"><span region="Default">Awak tak apa-apa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:50.610"
        end="01:01:53.790"><span region="Default">Begini rupanya rasa barang yang dihantar.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:53.800"
        end="01:01:55.540"><span region="Default">Jadi, di mana kita?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:56.470"
        end="01:01:58.390"><span region="Default">Ia seperti kembali ke rumahnya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:01:58.400"
        end="01:02:01.550"><span region="Default">Kalau macam ini, kita akan sampai di tempat Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:01.550"
        end="01:02:02.700"><span region="Default">Bagus.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:03.480"
        end="01:02:05.480"><span region="Default">Masa bergolek-golek lah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:11.540"
        end="01:02:14.450"><span region="Default">- Adakah itu Ariana?<br/>- Ariana bukannya jenis yang sanggup tendang anjing.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:14.450"
        end="01:02:18.320"><span region="Default">- Ariana lebih baik daripada itu. Ini bukan Ariana.<br/>- Jika itu memang Ariana, saya rasa kecewa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:18.460"
        end="01:02:20.790"><span region="Default">- Gaya apa yang dia cuba lakukan itu?<br/>- Berbeza dari saya bayangkan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:20.790"
        end="01:02:24.160"><span region="Default">- Saya nak tengok senyuman Ariana.<br/>- Itu tak sama seperti Ariana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:38.740"
        end="01:02:42.480"><span region="Default">♪ Aku tersenyum demi orang lain ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:42.480"
        end="01:02:45.050"><span region="Default">♪ Menjadi diri indahku, yang terpantul di mata semua orang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:46.260"
        end="01:02:52.990"><span region="Default">♪ Aku nak terus bersinar, tapi aku rasa sedikit kecewa ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:52.990"
        end="01:02:56.980"><span region="Default">♪ Aku tak nak diri aku dibenci ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:02:56.980"
        end="01:03:00.770"><span region="Default">♪ Aku cuma tak nak berseorangan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:00.780"
        end="01:03:02.500"><span region="Default">♪ Aku selalu jadi budak baik ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:02.500"
        end="01:03:06.510"><span region="Default">♪ Kadang-kala aku pun tak tahu ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:06.510"
        end="01:03:08.880"><span region="Default">♪ Nak buat apa lagi ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:09.200"
        end="01:03:14.250"><span region="Default">♪ Aku cuma ketawa dan ketawa, kan? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:14.260"
        end="01:03:16.970"><span region="Default">♪ Perasaan yang aku tinggalkan dulu ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:16.970"
        end="01:03:18.480"><span region="Default">♪ Kerap berulang sekarang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:18.480"
        end="01:03:21.710"><span region="Default">♪ Rasa samar-samar dalam hati aku ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:21.710"
        end="01:03:25.230"><span region="Default">♪ Membuat dada aku berasa sakit ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:25.230"
        end="01:03:30.210"><span region="Default">♪ Aku cuma ketawa dan ketawa, itu pasti betul ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:30.210"
        end="01:03:34.700"><span region="Default">♪ Perasaan berpura-pura tak lihat ia berulang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:34.700"
        end="01:03:37.970"><span region="Default">♪ Beritahu aku apa yang betul ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:37.970"
        end="01:03:40.200"><span region="Default">♪ Apa yang patut aku buat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:40.200"
        end="01:03:42.230"><span region="Default">♪ Apa yang patut aku buat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:42.230"
        end="01:03:44.000"><span region="Default">♪ Apa yang patut aku buat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:44.000"
        end="01:03:49.810"><span region="Default">♪ Apa yang aku patut buat sekarang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:54.910"
        end="01:03:56.140"><span region="Default">Kenapa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:03:56.780"
        end="01:03:59.580"><span region="Default">Festival ini sepatutnya rasa seronok.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:06.230"
        end="01:04:07.370"><span region="Default">Jangan risau.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:07.710"
        end="01:04:09.150"><span region="Default">Ini akan berhasil juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:09.630"
        end="01:04:12.910"><span region="Default">Nene, mari kita buat apa yang boleh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:14.140"
        end="01:04:15.190"><span region="Default">Betul itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:29.120"
        end="01:04:30.890"><span region="Default">Bangun, Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:33.800"
        end="01:04:35.020"><span region="Default">Hm?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:35.020"
        end="01:04:36.340"><span region="Default">Tempat apa itu?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:41.690"
        end="01:04:43.930"><span region="Default">Itu pastinya Bo…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:49.680"
        end="01:04:55.370"><span region="Default">Maharaja Bo mempersembahkan Festival Hiburan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:57.420"
        end="01:04:59.130"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:04:59.140"
        end="01:05:00.930"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:01.400"
        end="01:05:04.840"><span region="Default">♪ Maha, Maha, Maharaja Bo Bo Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:05.160"
        end="01:05:06.570"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:06.570"
        end="01:05:07.170"><span region="Default">♪ Bo! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:07.170"
        end="01:05:08.610"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:08.620"
        end="01:05:09.130"><span region="Default">♪ Bo! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:09.140"
        end="01:05:13.280"><span region="Default">♪ Cara, cara, cara, Bo, Bo, Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:13.280"
        end="01:05:17.310"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah, ini adalah, ini adalah Bo, Bo, Bo♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:17.310"
        end="01:05:18.890"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:18.890"
        end="01:05:20.670"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:21.060"
        end="01:05:25.350"><span region="Default">♪ Dunia ini ikut suka hati Maharaja Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:25.350"
        end="01:05:26.400"><span region="Default">Ini adalah Bo ♪ ♪ Dunia ini ikut suka hati Maharaja Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:26.410"
        end="01:05:28.890"><span region="Default">♪ Bo, Bo, Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:28.890"
        end="01:05:30.130"><span region="Default">♪ Cara, cara, cara ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:30.130"
        end="01:05:31.130"><span region="Default">♪ Cara, cara ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:31.130"
        end="01:05:32.150"><span region="Default">♪ Bo, Bo, Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:32.150"
        end="01:05:33.140"><span region="Default">♪ Bo! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:33.140"
        end="01:05:37.000"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah, ini adalah, Bo, Bo, Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:37.390"
        end="01:05:40.360"><span region="Default">♪ Aku tak perlu beratur di belakang orang lain! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:40.360"
        end="01:05:42.890"><span region="Default">♪ Bo sentiasa di depan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:42.890"
        end="01:05:44.650"><span region="Default">♪ Mengganas! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:45.080"
        end="01:05:48.230"><span region="Default">♪ Tiada siapa boleh hentikan kebebasan seseorang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:48.230"
        end="01:05:51.080"><span region="Default">♪ Ini satu letupan kari yang besar! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:51.590"
        end="01:05:53.130"><span region="Default">♪ Meletup! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:53.130"
        end="01:05:55.120"><span region="Default">♪ Makan minum gila-gila! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:55.120"
        end="01:05:57.120"><span region="Default">♪ Bo, Bo, Bo! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:57.120"
        end="01:05:58.850"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo, Bo♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:05:58.850"
        end="01:06:00.420"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:01.670"
        end="01:06:05.320"><span region="Default">♪ Dunia ini ikut suka hati Maharaja Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:05.320"
        end="01:06:07.110"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo, Bo♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:07.110"
        end="01:06:08.800"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:09.100"
        end="01:06:11.230"><span region="Default">♪ Cara, cara, cara ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:11.230"
        end="01:06:12.110"><span region="Default">♪ Bo, Bo, Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:12.110"
        end="01:06:13.040"><span region="Default">♪ Bo! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:13.040"
        end="01:06:15.070"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah, ini adalah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:15.070"
        end="01:06:17.270"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo, Bo, Bo! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:17.270"
        end="01:06:19.080"><span region="Default">♪ Aku boleh buat apa saja aku suka ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:19.500"
        end="01:06:22.170"><span region="Default">♪ Tidur mati macam kayu, hebatlah! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:22.170"
        end="01:06:23.510"><span region="Default">♪ Masa tengah malam ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:23.810"
        end="01:06:25.080"><span region="Default">♪ (Ikan Mola yang hilang kawalan) ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:25.080"
        end="01:06:27.050"><span region="Default">♪ Sudah tentu gigi tu ♪<br/>♪ Tak payah berus ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:27.060"
        end="01:06:28.830"><span region="Default">♪ (Tak berlubang ke nanti?) ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:28.830"
        end="01:06:30.110"><span region="Default">♪ Jangan risau ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:31.040"
        end="01:06:32.950"><span region="Default">♪ Itu gigi susu saja ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:32.960"
        end="01:06:35.020"><span region="Default">♪ (Begitu berlagak) ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:35.020"
        end="01:06:37.080"><span region="Default">♪ Bo, Bo, Bo! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:37.080"
        end="01:06:38.550"><span region="Default">♪ Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:38.550"
        end="01:06:40.540"><span region="Default">♪ Bo, Ini adalah Bo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:56.130"
        end="01:06:58.540"><span region="Default">Nene, kenapa kau tak menari?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:06:59.760"
        end="01:07:03.580"><span region="Default">Kazama, bukankah aku suruh kau tukar kostum pentas?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:05.690"
        end="01:07:07.130"><span region="Default">Kamu dah janji, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:07.570"
        end="01:07:09.390"><span region="Default">Kita semua akan menari.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:11.770"
        end="01:07:12.820"><span region="Default">Menari.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:12.820"
        end="01:07:13.950"><span region="Default">- Tak nak!<br/>- Tak nak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:14.290"
        end="01:07:15.430"><span region="Default">Kita ini kawan, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:15.910"
        end="01:07:18.390"><span region="Default">Sebab kita kawan, aku nak beritahu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:18.400"
        end="01:07:21.420"><span region="Default">Perasaan orang lain bukan boleh ikut suka hati kita.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:21.420"
        end="01:07:24.980"><span region="Default">Kami takkan biar sesiapa pun suruh kami menari.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:26.150"
        end="01:07:27.690"><span region="Default">Jika kamu tak menari,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:27.700"
        end="01:07:30.490"><span region="Default">baik pergi potong bawang saja!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:32.500"
        end="01:07:33.750"><span region="Default">Kazama!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:34.260"
        end="01:07:36.110"><span region="Default">Mama!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:36.110"
        end="01:07:38.390"><span region="Default">Toru!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:38.390"
        end="01:07:39.400"><span region="Default">Huh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:44.740"
        end="01:07:45.880"><span region="Default">Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:45.880"
        end="01:07:47.080"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:47.460"
        end="01:07:48.730"><span region="Default">Awak tak apa-apa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:50.530"
        end="01:07:53.340"><span region="Default">Boleh tak awak muncul secara normal lain kali?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:53.340"
        end="01:07:55.450"><span region="Default">Hei! Apa yang dah jadi ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:55.450"
        end="01:07:57.990"><span region="Default">Saya dah suruh awak buang benda ini jauh-jauh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:07:58.000"
        end="01:08:00.420"><span region="Default">Tak mungkin saya akan buang Hanagelina ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:00.420"
        end="01:08:02.310"><span region="Default">Kazama, jahatnya kau.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:04.340"
        end="01:08:05.730"><span region="Default">Bagus!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:11.050"
        end="01:08:12.730"><span region="Default">Selamat datang ke festival ini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:12.730"
        end="01:08:16.520"><span region="Default">Ada suatu yang berubah pada awak sejak kali terakhir kita bertemu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:16.939"
        end="01:08:19.240"><span region="Default">Sebab budak-budak cepat membesar.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:19.910"
        end="01:08:20.990"><span region="Default">Shin-chan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:20.990"
        end="01:08:22.840"><span region="Default">Boleh serah kertas itu pada aku?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:23.300"
        end="01:08:24.310"><span region="Default">Dan…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:24.590"
        end="01:08:27.040"><span region="Default">mari kita menari semua!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:31.090"
        end="01:08:32.090"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:32.550"
        end="01:08:33.779"><span region="Default">Shin-chan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:33.779"
        end="01:08:34.870"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:34.870"
        end="01:08:35.880"><span region="Default">Shin-chan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:35.880"
        end="01:08:38.630"><span region="Default">Aku nak tengok hingus Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:39.279"
        end="01:08:41.080"><span region="Default">Hingus itu dah…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:41.080"
        end="01:08:42.479"><span region="Default">Tak keluar dah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:44.609"
        end="01:08:45.890"><span region="Default">Berikan kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:46.260"
        end="01:08:47.479"><span region="Default">Tak nak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:08:58.310"
        end="01:09:00.370"><span region="Default">Itu adalah kuasa kertas…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:00.830"
        end="01:09:01.819"><span region="Default">Shin-chan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:01.819"
        end="01:09:03.560"><span region="Default">Arah sini, Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:07.149"
        end="01:09:10.710"><span region="Default">Boleh tak kau masukkan kertas yang lain itu</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:10.710"
        end="01:09:12.189"><span region="Default">di lubang kiri ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:12.189"
        end="01:09:13.279"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:13.279"
        end="01:09:15.660"><span region="Default">Ini langsung tak menyeronokkan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:17.180"
        end="01:09:18.680"><span region="Default">Tak menyeronokkan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:20.870"
        end="01:09:23.569"><span region="Default">Semua itu disebabkan kau tak cukup kuat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:24.430"
        end="01:09:26.710"><span region="Default">Jika kau nak tunaikan keinginan kau,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:26.710"
        end="01:09:28.830"><span region="Default">kau perlukan kuasa yang kuat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:33.810"
        end="01:09:34.950"><span region="Default">Shin-chan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:35.580"
        end="01:09:36.689"><span region="Default">Tak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:36.689"
        end="01:09:38.390"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke Nohara!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:39.479"
        end="01:09:41.040"><span region="Default">Berikan aku kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:41.600"
        end="01:09:42.710"><span region="Default">Bo…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:43.189"
        end="01:09:45.770"><span region="Default">Menyeronokkan atau tidak…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:45.770"
        end="01:09:47.779"><span region="Default">Aku tak kisah semua itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:48.359"
        end="01:09:50.510"><span region="Default">Aku cuma inginkan kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:51.330"
        end="01:09:55.690"><span region="Default">Sebab aku akan sempurna jika dapat kepingan yang lain!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:09:57.890"
        end="01:09:59.060"><span region="Default">Macam mana ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:01.370"
        end="01:10:02.210"><span region="Default">Shiro?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:08.240"
        end="01:10:09.430"><span region="Default">Masao?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:24.310"
        end="01:10:25.680"><span region="Default">Dia bilas hidungnya?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:26.230"
        end="01:10:28.350"><span region="Default">Tapi ia lakukan suatu yang hebat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:28.960"
        end="01:10:30.620"><span region="Default">Masao!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:34.690"
        end="01:10:35.710"><span region="Default">Hei!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:38.600"
        end="01:10:40.610"><span region="Default">- Sekarang, mari lari!<br/>- Ya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:47.780"
        end="01:10:51.350"><span region="Default">Gunakan kuasa penuh kamu bagi menangkap Shinnosuke Nohara!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:51.350"
        end="01:10:55.290"><span region="Default">Binatang Pembunuh. Mod Bertarung. Tahap maksimum!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:10:59.530"
        end="01:11:02.990"><span region="Default">Itu dah melampau. Dia cuma budak-budak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:03.490"
        end="01:11:05.860"><span region="Default">Jangan pandang rendah Shinnosuke Nohara.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:06.640"
        end="01:11:09.920"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke Nohara boleh buat ribut dengan kentutnya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:09.930"
        end="01:11:12.010"><span region="Default">Dan hancurkan banyak benda dengan punggung.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:13.260"
        end="01:11:15.750"><span region="Default">Aku akan pastikan dapat kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:20.310"
        end="01:11:22.370"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke, siapa pula gadis itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:22.900"
        end="01:11:24.380"><span region="Default">Dia Ariana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:24.910"
        end="01:11:26.010"><span region="Default">Alahai.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:47.520"
        end="01:11:48.900"><span region="Default">Macam mana ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:49.700"
        end="01:11:52.080"><span region="Default">Masao, kenapa awak berlagak macam anjing?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:53.000"
        end="01:11:57.000"><span region="Default">Awak takkan faham perasaan seseorang yang bertahan hidup dengan menjadi anjing!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:11:58.070"
        end="01:12:01.490"><span region="Default">Kertas di hidung Bo-chan semakin lama semakin dalam.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:02.070"
        end="01:12:05.710"><span region="Default">Kita kena tariknya cepat. Itu bukannya Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:06.660"
        end="01:12:08.710"><span region="Default">Bo patutnya lebih lemah-lembut.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:08.710"
        end="01:12:12.790"><span region="Default">Dia seorang baik hati dan prihatin pada yang lain.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:12.790"
        end="01:12:15.960"><span region="Default">Bo tanpa ada hingus bukanlah Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:16.880"
        end="01:12:19.750"><span region="Default">Bo memang kena sentiasa berhingus ke?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:20.070"
        end="01:12:21.100"><span region="Default">Eh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:21.490"
        end="01:12:23.390"><span region="Default">"Macam Bo" itu maksudnya apa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:23.390"
        end="01:12:26.850"><span region="Default">Adakah dia mesti sentiasa baik hati, sentiasa jadi budak baik?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:26.850"
        end="01:12:30.530"><span region="Default">Dan juga bukankah semua orang<br/>yang paksa tentukan untuk dia?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:31.020"
        end="01:12:33.360"><span region="Default">Walaupun diri dia sendiri langsung tak rasa seronok,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:33.360"
        end="01:12:36.720"><span region="Default">adakah kena tahan demi orang lain dan tetap senyum?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:36.720"
        end="01:12:39.010"><span region="Default">Itu pasti menjengkelkan dan buatnya marah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:39.010"
        end="01:12:40.600"><span region="Default">Masa takut sampai nak menangis pun,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:40.600"
        end="01:12:43.280"><span region="Default">kena pura-pura tak apa dan senyum juga ke!?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:44.700"
        end="01:12:46.170"><span region="Default">Aku cemburu,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:46.170"
        end="01:12:47.600"><span region="Default">walaupun buat ikut suka hati,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:47.600"
        end="01:12:49.890"><span region="Default">tetap disokong semua orang,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:49.890"
        end="01:12:51.110"><span region="Default">tak dibenci pun….</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:52.590"
        end="01:12:54.350"><span region="Default">Walaupun langsung bukan budak baik,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:12:54.360"
        end="01:12:56.550"><span region="Default">tapi sekarang mungkin lebih bahagia kan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:00.340"
        end="01:13:02.480"><span region="Default">Tak… begini…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:03.400"
        end="01:13:04.480"><span region="Default">Maaf.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:05.670"
        end="01:13:08.000"><span region="Default">Adakah Bo rasa bahagia?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:08.000"
        end="01:13:10.070"><span region="Default">Bo tanpa ada hingus mengalir itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:11.070"
        end="01:13:12.800"><span region="Default">Jika Bo rasa gembira,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:12.800"
        end="01:13:15.130"><span region="Default">baik kita jangan tarik kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:17.240"
        end="01:13:20.790"><span region="Default">Apa yang kita tahu pasal Bo ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:34.100"
        end="01:13:35.830"><span region="Default">Kita kena pergi sekarang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:46.760"
        end="01:13:47.780"><span region="Default">Orang dewasa dah hilang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:47.780"
        end="01:13:48.850"><span region="Default">Mereka dah lari?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:49.350"
        end="01:13:51.740"><span region="Default">Tapi kenapa tak bawa budak ini sekali?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:13:53.010"
        end="01:13:54.490"><span region="Default">Betul juga itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:15.910"
        end="01:14:17.720"><span region="Default">Mata aku! Mata aku!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:18.960"
        end="01:14:20.820"><span region="Default">Dapat! Ini kuncinya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:21.180"
        end="01:14:22.290"><span region="Default">Bagus!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:27.870"
        end="01:14:30.840"><span region="Default">Pertama, kita kena selamatkan Nene dan Kazama.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:30.840"
        end="01:14:31.870"><span region="Default">Ya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:35.690"
        end="01:14:37.120"><span region="Default">Pelarian ditemui!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:37.120"
        end="01:14:39.390"><span region="Default">Menuju belah barat di taman tengah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:39.390"
        end="01:14:41.220"><span region="Default">Saya ulangi, pelarian ditemui!!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:41.230"
        end="01:14:43.450"><span region="Default">Menuju belah barat di taman tengah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:47.340"
        end="01:14:49.970"><span region="Default">Ini stoking saya sepanjang di India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:54.750"
        end="01:14:55.810"><span region="Default">Bagus!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:14:59.970"
        end="01:15:01.670"><span region="Default">Ini tak mungkin…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:01.670"
        end="01:15:03.660"><span region="Default">Stoking saya tak berkesan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:03.660"
        end="01:15:05.900"><span region="Default">Mungkin sebab terlalu lama buat kari,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:05.900"
        end="01:15:07.930"><span region="Default">bau rempah itu dah tutup bau busuk</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:07.930"
        end="01:15:10.340"><span region="Default">terus jadi wangi pedas sikit?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:10.920"
        end="01:15:12.290"><span region="Default">Ia tetap busuk bagi saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:12.640"
        end="01:15:14.900"><span region="Default">Rempah ini memang menyeramkan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:22.780"
        end="01:15:24.790"><span region="Default">Budak-budak itu sedang tunggu kita.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:24.790"
        end="01:15:27.710"><span region="Default">Kita tak boleh buat silap di sini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:32.710"
        end="01:15:34.000"><span region="Default">Tolonglah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:34.650"
        end="01:15:36.780"><span region="Default">Kuasa yang terpendam dalam badan saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:37.810"
        end="01:15:41.230"><span region="Default">Bangkitlah! Kuasa India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:41.230"
        end="01:15:44.420"><span region="Default">♪ Nama aku ialah Misae Nohara ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:44.430"
        end="01:15:47.640"><span region="Default">♪ Anak perempuan Koyama Yoshiji dan Hisae ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:47.640"
        end="01:15:50.410"><span region="Default">♪ Aku lahir di Kumamoto lalu pindah ke Tokyo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:50.410"
        end="01:15:52.840"><span region="Default">♪ Kemudian kahwin dengan Hiroshi ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:53.960"
        end="01:15:57.260"><span region="Default">♪ Menjadi ibu pada Shinnosuke dan Himawari ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:57.820"
        end="01:15:59.610"><span region="Default">Dan di India,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:15:59.610"
        end="01:16:03.890"><span region="Default">Nyawa Nene, Masao, Toru, Bo dipercayakan pada aku</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:03.890"
        end="01:16:06.230"><span region="Default">Sebab itu, aku akan jadi pahlawan terkuat</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:06.810"
        end="01:16:08.820"><span region="Default">Ke tepi kamu semua</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:11.540"
        end="01:16:13.840"><span region="Default">♪ Wow, wow, wow ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:13.840"
        end="01:16:15.420"><span region="Default">♪ Wow ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:15.420"
        end="01:16:17.820"><span region="Default">♪ Aku akan buka laluan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:17.830"
        end="01:16:21.540"><span region="Default">♪Wow, wow, wow ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:21.540"
        end="01:16:26.980"><span region="Default">♪ Misae Nohara nak lalu ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:27.940"
        end="01:16:31.650"><span region="Default">Kuasa India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:35.970"
        end="01:16:37.040"><span region="Default">Kenapa itu, Shiro?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:38.800"
        end="01:16:40.110"><span region="Default">Sifu Shiro!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:44.730"
        end="01:16:45.700"><span region="Default">Shiro?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:45.700"
        end="01:16:46.710"><span region="Default">Eh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:50.470"
        end="01:16:51.530"><span region="Default">Shiro!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:54.260"
        end="01:16:55.610"><span region="Default">Shiro!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:16:56.700"
        end="01:16:58.000"><span region="Default">Masao?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:01.570"
        end="01:17:03.240"><span region="Default">Masao!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:03.240"
        end="01:17:05.920"><span region="Default">Mama! Papa!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:06.260"
        end="01:17:08.810"><span region="Default">Aku takut sangat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:09.890"
        end="01:17:11.440"><span region="Default">Ayah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:12.100"
        end="01:17:13.790"><span region="Default">Ibu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:14.600"
        end="01:17:16.170"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:17.670"
        end="01:17:20.950"><span region="Default">Nene! Kazama! Dan juga Shiro!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:20.950"
        end="01:17:22.970"><span region="Default">Syukurlah kamu tak apa-apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:25.900"
        end="01:17:29.330"><span region="Default">Ayah dan ibu itu yang selalu saja sesat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:29.330"
        end="01:17:30.640"><span region="Default">Awak tak cedera?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:32.240"
        end="01:17:35.320"><span region="Default">Dari tadi awak cakap begitu, apa juga maksudnya?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:35.320"
        end="01:17:37.120"><span region="Default">Itu kata-kata baru saya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:37.120"
        end="01:17:38.610"><span region="Default">Saya pun tak tahu maksudnya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:38.610"
        end="01:17:40.900"><span region="Default">Tapi orang India kerap kata begitu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:41.750"
        end="01:17:43.420"><span region="Default">Awak tak tahu maksudnya?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:43.420"
        end="01:17:46.640"><span region="Default">Dhanyavaad itu bermaksud "terima kasih" dalam Jepun.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:48.170"
        end="01:17:50.700"><span region="Default">Terima kasih dah beritahu saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:50.710"
        end="01:17:52.870"><span region="Default">Patutnya "Dhanyavaad".</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:52.870"
        end="01:17:55.310"><span region="Default">Cuma "terima kasih" saja, dah sampai sejauh ni?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:17:55.720"
        end="01:17:58.800"><span region="Default">Walau dia masih budak, dia sangat kuat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:00.810"
        end="01:18:01.860"><span region="Default">Awak ini siapa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:02.720"
        end="01:18:05.400"><span region="Default">Ariana ini kawan saya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:05.400"
        end="01:18:06.410"><span region="Default">Kawan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:07.560"
        end="01:18:10.180"><span region="Default">Awak pasti yang dah selamatkan Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:10.760"
        end="01:18:12.020"><span region="Default">Terima kasih!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:12.760"
        end="01:18:14.410"><span region="Default">Terima kasih banyak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:15.740"
        end="01:18:16.880"><span region="Default">Tak apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:26.760"
        end="01:18:28.850"><span region="Default">Alamak! Lari cepat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:53.740"
        end="01:18:55.840"><span region="Default">Tak guna! Mereka dapat kejar!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:18:58.020"
        end="01:19:00.040"><span region="Default">Serahkan pada saya…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:00.040"
        end="01:19:01.420"><span region="Default">Dan teruskan…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:03.480"
        end="01:19:04.930"><span region="Default">Awak nampak penat…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:06.110"
        end="01:19:09.870"><span region="Default">Lari… bawa budak-budak itu ke tempat selamat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:19.320"
        end="01:19:21.100"><span region="Default">Seperti yang awak kata, abang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:22.710"
        end="01:19:25.480"><span region="Default">Lari! Bawa budak-budak itu ke tempat selamat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:26.970"
        end="01:19:28.390"><span region="Default">Operasi penyamaran saya…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:29.300"
        end="01:19:30.530"><span region="Default">dah berjaya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:32.060"
        end="01:19:33.690"><span region="Default">Awak terselamat?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:34.000"
        end="01:19:35.080"><span region="Default">Sudah tentu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:35.710"
        end="01:19:39.430"><span region="Default">Sebab saya tak percaya yang awak boleh kalah semudah itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:39.430"
        end="01:19:40.860"><span region="Default">Seperti dijangka, abang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:41.740"
        end="01:19:42.590"><span region="Default">Dill!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:42.590"
        end="01:19:46.490"><span region="Default">Kabir Katchapapal Pakkapapal Katchapapal Pakkapapal!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:53.270"
        end="01:19:56.090"><span region="Default">♪ Mari nyanyikan! Kuasa India! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:56.100"
        end="01:19:58.980"><span region="Default">♪ Boleh kau rasakan dalam diri aku ini?! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:19:58.980"
        end="01:20:01.390"><span region="Default">♪ Mari menari! Kuasa India! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:01.400"
        end="01:20:04.660"><span region="Default">Masuk sini! Sekarang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:04.660"
        end="01:20:07.530"><span region="Default">♪ Terus mara di jalan yang belum diketahui ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:07.530"
        end="01:20:11.630"><span region="Default">♪ Kami panas! Seperti super kari pedas! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:16.530"
        end="01:20:17.930"><span region="Default">Ini seperti gudang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:19.170"
        end="01:20:20.940"><span region="Default">Mari kita naik kereta itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:22.830"
        end="01:20:24.780"><span region="Default">Kenapa ini, Shin-chan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:24.780"
        end="01:20:27.160"><span region="Default">Aku nak pergi ke tempat Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:27.160"
        end="01:20:28.480"><span region="Default">Eh?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:28.890"
        end="01:20:31.900"><span region="Default">Aku tak nak lari dan tinggalkan Bo sendiri!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:37.240"
        end="01:20:38.320"><span region="Default">Betul itu…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:38.650"
        end="01:20:43.090"><span region="Default">Sebab itu kita lari sekarang bagi selamatkan Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:43.880"
        end="01:20:46.230"><span region="Default">Kita tak boleh beri dia kertas itu, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:46.910"
        end="01:20:50.200"><span region="Default">Bagi hentikan Bo untuk sakiti sesiapa lagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:52.270"
        end="01:20:53.270"><span region="Default">Ya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:54.650"
        end="01:20:56.380"><span region="Default">Jadi, kita nak lari mana?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:20:58.120"
        end="01:21:00.490"><span region="Default">- Ini tak boleh!<br/>- Mereka terlalu ramai!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:00.490"
        end="01:21:02.460"><span region="Default">Kita takkan boleh lari.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:06.800"
        end="01:21:08.220"><span region="Default">Macam mana ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:09.060"
        end="01:21:10.490"><span region="Default">Mari pergi, semua!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:12.890"
        end="01:21:14.610"><span region="Default">Naik sini!!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:15.620"
        end="01:21:17.630"><span region="Default">Eh?!!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:18.120"
        end="01:21:20.150"><span region="Default">Awak boleh pandu kapal terbang?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:20.150"
        end="01:21:25.180"><span region="Default">Aku ini ada bakat terpendam, dan aku akan ledakkan sampai 120%!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:27.290"
        end="01:21:29.800"><span region="Default">Mari pergi! Kuasa India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:46.730"
        end="01:21:48.270"><span region="Default">♪ Pa-pa-panaskan engin kau ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:48.270"
        end="01:21:52.780"><span region="Default">♪ Dengar ia mengaum, mengaum, mengaum ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:52.780"
        end="01:21:54.400"><span region="Default">♪ Logam penuh tekanan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:54.400"
        end="01:21:58.730"><span region="Default">♪ Rayu kau sentuh lalu pergi, pergi, pergi ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:21:58.980"
        end="01:22:03.730"><span region="Default">♪ Ini lebuhraya ke zon bahaya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:05.050"
        end="01:22:10.730"><span region="Default">♪ Menerjah masuk ke zon bahaya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:10.730"
        end="01:22:13.060"><span region="Default">Kuasa India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:13.060"
        end="01:22:14.230"><span region="Default">Jangan harap boleh lari!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:14.230"
        end="01:22:15.760"><span region="Default">♪ Menuju ke senja ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:15.760"
        end="01:22:19.980"><span region="Default">♪ Kembangkan sayapnya malam ini… ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:20.300"
        end="01:22:25.350"><span region="Default">♪Na, na, na, na, terus pecut habis♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:25.350"
        end="01:22:26.820"><span region="Default">Cepat lagi, ayah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:26.820"
        end="01:22:31.230"><span region="Default">♪ Ini lebuhraya ke zon bahaya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:32.290"
        end="01:22:38.590"><span region="Default">♪ Menerjah masuk ke zon bahaya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:41.870"
        end="01:22:43.210"><span region="Default">♪ Lah, lah, lah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:44.180"
        end="01:22:46.870"><span region="Default">♪ Lah, lah, lah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:46.870"
        end="01:22:49.940"><span region="Default">♪ Lah, lah, lah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:49.940"
        end="01:22:53.910"><span region="Default">♪ Ho, ho, yo, yo, yo ,yo ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:53.910"
        end="01:22:57.170"><span region="Default">♪ Go ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:58.510"
        end="01:22:59.810"><span region="Default">Biar orang aku kejar guna—</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:22:59.810"
        end="01:23:01.010"><span region="Default">Aku pergi sendiri!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:08.560"
        end="01:23:14.930"><span region="Default">♪ Lah, lah, lah, lah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:14.930"
        end="01:23:17.000"><span region="Default">Cepat ikut rakan seiring aku itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:21.390"
        end="01:23:23.080"><span region="Default">♪ Di tepi jurang ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:23.080"
        end="01:23:27.140"><span region="Default">♪ Situlah tempat yang aku selalu rindu nak berada ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:27.480"
        end="01:23:29.230"><span region="Default">♪ Semakin jauh ke tepi jurang, ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:29.230"
        end="01:23:31.720"><span region="Default">♪ semakin membara rasa ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:33.640"
        end="01:23:38.790"><span region="Default">♪ Ini lebuhraya ke zon bahaya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:39.120"
        end="01:23:44.880"><span region="Default">♪ Akan bawa masuk ke zon bahaya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:45.940"
        end="01:23:50.330"><span region="Default">♪ Ini lebuhraya ke zon bahaya ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:50.340"
        end="01:23:51.570"><span region="Default">Apa jadi ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:52.790"
        end="01:23:54.340"><span region="Default">Huh? Alamak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:23:54.350"
        end="01:23:56.520"><span region="Default">Minyak kita dalam zon bahaya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:16.500"
        end="01:24:19.330"><span region="Default">Dari zon bahaya ke tebing sungai…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:20.220"
        end="01:24:21.750"><span region="Default">Sayang tak apa-apa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:25.460"
        end="01:24:26.470"><span region="Default">Apa itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:27.130"
        end="01:24:28.270"><span region="Default">Burung?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:28.270"
        end="01:24:29.700"><span region="Default">Kapal terbang?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:29.700"
        end="01:24:30.980"><span region="Default">Itu Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:35.870"
        end="01:24:37.600"><span region="Default">Bunga Api!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:37.600"
        end="01:24:38.990"><span region="Default">Ini bukan masanya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:39.770"
        end="01:24:41.290"><span region="Default">Kamu dah faham, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:41.300"
        end="01:24:43.130"><span region="Default">Kamu tak boleh lari daripada aku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:43.660"
        end="01:24:45.330"><span region="Default">Berikan aku kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:48.110"
        end="01:24:49.980"><span region="Default">Kami tak boleh biarkan itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:49.980"
        end="01:24:52.720"><span region="Default">Bo, ini untuk melindungi awak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:52.720"
        end="01:24:53.810"><span region="Default">Betul itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:55.170"
        end="01:24:58.450"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke! Bawa kertas itu dan lari jauh dari sini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:58.450"
        end="01:25:00.680"><span region="Default">Kami akan cuba lengahkan dia!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:10.660"
        end="01:25:13.740"><span region="Default">Kazama! Nene! Masao!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:13.740"
        end="01:25:14.940"><span region="Default">Kamu semua!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:15.360"
        end="01:25:17.060"><span region="Default">Jangan nak mengacau!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:21.450"
        end="01:25:24.900"><span region="Default">Dua kepingan itu akan buat aku jadi sempurna.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:25.590"
        end="01:25:27.640"><span region="Default">Pilih, Shinnosuke Nohara!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:28.170"
        end="01:25:30.350"><span region="Default">Adakah kau nak serah kertas itu sendiri?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:30.360"
        end="01:25:32.910"><span region="Default">Atau aku yang rampas daripada kau?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:37.720"
        end="01:25:38.850"><span region="Default">Jangan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:38.850"
        end="01:25:39.980"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:45.440"
        end="01:25:49.460"><span region="Default">Ini untuk dapatkan semula kertas dari hidung Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:50.240"
        end="01:25:52.820"><span region="Default">Jangan kata awak nak lekat itu di hidung awak?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:52.820"
        end="01:25:54.370"><span region="Default">Hentikannya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:59.690"
        end="01:26:00.820"><span region="Default">Di punggung?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:17.930"
        end="01:26:19.440"><span region="Default">Kertas itu di punggung…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:19.440"
        end="01:26:21.440"><span region="Default">Saya tak pernah terfikir itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:21.440"
        end="01:26:23.580"><span region="Default">Dengan letaknya dalam punggung</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:23.580"
        end="01:26:25.090"><span region="Default">dan bukan tercucuk di hidung,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:25.090"
        end="01:26:26.880"><span region="Default">orang itu boleh dapatkan kuasa</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:26.880"
        end="01:26:29.870"><span region="Default">tanpa kuasa jahat itu mengawalnya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:29.880"
        end="01:26:31.230"><span region="Default">Seperti dijangka, abang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:31.230"
        end="01:26:32.910"><span region="Default">Awak ada pemerhatian yang bagus.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:32.910"
        end="01:26:35.540"><span region="Default">Lakukannya! Dapatkan semula kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:35.540"
        end="01:26:37.700"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke Si Budak Comel!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:37.700"
        end="01:26:39.000"><span region="Default">Sini saya tarik kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:39.000"
        end="01:26:39.980"><span region="Default">Tak nak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:39.980"
        end="01:26:41.230"><span region="Default">Aku nak kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:41.230"
        end="01:26:42.950"><span region="Default">Tak nak! Tak nak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:45.600"
        end="01:26:46.910"><span region="Default">Aku nak kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:46.910"
        end="01:26:47.960"><span region="Default">Tak nak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:49.840"
        end="01:26:51.010"><span region="Default">Buang kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:51.010"
        end="01:26:52.590"><span region="Default">Tak nak! Aku nak kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:52.590"
        end="01:26:53.620"><span region="Default">Tak nak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:54.160"
        end="01:26:55.690"><span region="Default">- Aku nak kertas itu!<br/>- Buang kertas itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:55.690"
        end="01:26:58.730"><span region="Default">- Tak nak! Tak nak! Tak nak!<br/>- Tak nak! Tak nak! Tak nak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:58.730"
        end="01:27:00.170"><span region="Default">Tak nak!!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:02.600"
        end="01:27:04.330"><span region="Default">Bo, awak tak apa-apa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:05.940"
        end="01:27:07.660"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke Nohara.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:07.660"
        end="01:27:10.830"><span region="Default">Kau memang bukan orang biasa-biasa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:10.830"
        end="01:27:13.340"><span region="Default">Tapi aksi sebenar bermula di sini.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:18.540"
        end="01:27:19.510"><span region="Default">Habislah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:19.510"
        end="01:27:21.140"><span region="Default">Kertas itu dah masuk sepenuhnya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:21.140"
        end="01:27:22.840"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke Si Budak Comel!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:22.840"
        end="01:27:25.060"><span region="Default">Lari dari sana!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:44.350"
        end="01:27:45.400"><span region="Default">Bo…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:46.170"
        end="01:27:49.330"><span region="Default">Aku dah sempurna sekarang…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:49.800"
        end="01:27:51.920"><span region="Default">Kuasa India…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:51.920"
        end="01:27:52.980"><span region="Default">Lambat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:53.340"
        end="01:27:54.710"><span region="Default">Seperti kamu tak gerak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:59.670"
        end="01:28:01.370"><span region="Default">Raja zalim dah lahir.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:01.370"
        end="01:28:02.480"><span region="Default">Malangnya…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:02.480"
        end="01:28:06.300"><span region="Default">Jika ini terjadi, takkan ada orang boleh hentikannya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:22.330"
        end="01:28:23.660"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:27.360"
        end="01:28:29.170"><span region="Default">Shinnosuke!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:29.170"
        end="01:28:30.600"><span region="Default">Cukuplah itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:32.300"
        end="01:28:36.290"><span region="Default">Aku pasti dapat tarik kertas itu…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:36.290"
        end="01:28:38.520"><span region="Default">Sebab saya teringin nak lihat…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:38.520"
        end="01:28:40.560"><span region="Default">Bo dengan hingus.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:40.560"
        end="01:28:41.850"><span region="Default">Aku dah kata.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:41.850"
        end="01:28:44.270"><span region="Default">Dah tiada hingus.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:44.270"
        end="01:28:46.650"><span region="Default">Bo, awak patut keluarkannya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:46.650"
        end="01:28:48.680"><span region="Default">Walau tiada hingus itu,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:48.680"
        end="01:28:51.480"><span region="Default">awak tetap menyeronokkan bagi saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:51.480"
        end="01:28:53.250"><span region="Default">Cuma Bo sekarang ini,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:53.250"
        end="01:28:55.860"><span region="Default">langsung tak menyeronokkan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:55.860"
        end="01:28:58.000"><span region="Default">Apa yang kau tahu pasal diri aku?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:58.000"
        end="01:28:59.970"><span region="Default">Biar saya beritahu awak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:59.980"
        end="01:29:02.000"><span region="Default">Bo, awak nak main apa?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:02.010"
        end="01:29:05.580"><span region="Default">Awak nak pergi mana? Nak makan apa? Apa yang awak suka?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:05.580"
        end="01:29:06.680"><span region="Default">Hentikannya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:07.250"
        end="01:29:09.940"><span region="Default">Sia-sia saja jika kau cuba nak kalahkan aku.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:10.530"
        end="01:29:12.890"><span region="Default">Aku bukannya nak kalahkan awak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:13.730"
        end="01:29:16.500"><span region="Default">Aku cuma nak bermain dengan awak…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:17.700"
        end="01:29:24.400"><span region="Default">Walau awak dah jadi Si Zalim Bo, Paus Bo atau Raja Bo,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:24.400"
        end="01:29:26.960"><span region="Default">Saya tetap nak bermain dengan awak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:27.750"
        end="01:29:29.300"><span region="Default">Betul itu, Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:29.310"
        end="01:29:30.690"><span region="Default">Marilah bermain.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:30.690"
        end="01:29:32.270"><span region="Default">Ia akan jadi menyeronokkan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:33.380"
        end="01:29:36.130"><span region="Default">Walau awak dah tiada hingus mengalir…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:36.130"
        end="01:29:37.580"><span region="Default">Walau awak dah berubah,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:37.580"
        end="01:29:40.000"><span region="Default">aku tetap nak main dengan awak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:40.000"
        end="01:29:41.880"><span region="Default">Kita akan bermain selamanya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:42.560"
        end="01:29:44.980"><span region="Default">Mari bermain, Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:44.980"
        end="01:29:46.060"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:46.060"
        end="01:29:47.150"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:47.150"
        end="01:29:48.540"><span region="Default">Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:02.150"
        end="01:30:05.320"><span region="Default">Bo. Mari menari bersama…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:13.070"
        end="01:30:15.170"><span region="Default">(Upacara Kemasukan Tadika Futaba)</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:05.640"
        end="01:31:08.060"><span region="Default">Mari kita menari bersama, Bo.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:08.060"
        end="01:31:09.690"><span region="Default">Sebab kita semua…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:10.780"
        end="01:31:13.030"><span region="Default">adalah kawan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:13.030"
        end="01:31:15.320"><span region="Default">Kan! Kata gajah ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:58.170"
        end="01:32:00.350"><span region="Default">Batu berbentuk punggung…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:00.350"
        end="01:32:02.250"><span region="Default">Sipi rambutku dari India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:02.250"
        end="01:32:04.690"><span region="Default">Itu cenderamata.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:04.700"
        end="01:32:06.030"><span region="Default">Sama macam.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:06.030"
        end="01:32:07.560"><span region="Default">Macam sama.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:11.300"
        end="01:32:12.490"><span region="Default">Itu Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:12.490"
        end="01:32:14.170"><span region="Default">- Bo! Bo!<br/>- Bo!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:14.170"
        end="01:32:16.220"><span region="Default">Bo menangis itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:16.220"
        end="01:32:17.190"><span region="Default">Taklah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:17.190"
        end="01:32:18.380"><span region="Default">Ini hingus.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:21.000"
        end="01:32:23.700"><span region="Default">Kamu semua, maafkan saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:34.980"
        end="01:32:36.020"><span region="Default">Bagusnya…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:36.910"
        end="01:32:38.580"><span region="Default">Walau dia dah jadi raja zalim,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:38.580"
        end="01:32:41.140"><span region="Default">dia masih ada kawan yang sayangkan dia.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:41.830"
        end="01:32:45.800"><span region="Default">Sepatutnya aku kena gembira bersama mereka dengan senyuman…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:46.470"
        end="01:32:50.650"><span region="Default">Tapi aku rasa cemburu sangat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:51.750"
        end="01:32:55.230"><span region="Default">Diri saya ini teruknya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:59.160"
        end="01:33:01.820"><span region="Default">Jika semua tahu betapa buruk perangai saya,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:01.820"
        end="01:33:04.190"><span region="Default">pasti akan benci saya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:04.980"
        end="01:33:06.230"><span region="Default">Maksud saya…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:06.790"
        end="01:33:08.020"><span region="Default">Saya kata apa ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:08.860"
        end="01:33:11.500"><span region="Default">Saya pula sukakan diri awak itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:11.500"
        end="01:33:12.480"><span region="Default">Eh?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:12.480"
        end="01:33:16.470"><span region="Default">Memang bagus dapat tersenyum dan buat orang lain gembira,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:16.470"
        end="01:33:18.450"><span region="Default">tapi ada masanya tak boleh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:18.450"
        end="01:33:19.290"><span region="Default">Kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:19.300"
        end="01:33:20.390"><span region="Default">Ya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:20.390"
        end="01:33:22.480"><span region="Default">Ia sangat sukar untuk disukai</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:22.480"
        end="01:33:25.810"><span region="Default">oleh ramai orang dengan cuba jadi baik.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:25.810"
        end="01:33:27.410"><span region="Default">Dan tak buat kesilapan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:27.990"
        end="01:33:30.710"><span region="Default">Tiada manusia yang sempurna itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:30.710"
        end="01:33:32.380"><span region="Default">Kalau awak terlalu sempurna,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:32.380"
        end="01:33:33.640"><span region="Default">saya takkan boleh bersama awak...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:33.640"
        end="01:33:34.890"><span region="Default">Sebab ia cuma buat saya rasa penat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:34.900"
        end="01:33:36.500"><span region="Default">Saya pun sama.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:36.500"
        end="01:33:38.040"><span region="Default">Jika awak seorang yang berperangai baik,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:38.040"
        end="01:33:39.880"><span region="Default">cantik, bergaya mantap,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:39.880"
        end="01:33:41.880"><span region="Default">sentiasa lembut, mesra dengan semua orang,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:41.880"
        end="01:33:43.410"><span region="Default">dan pandai buat apa saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:43.410"
        end="01:33:45.140"><span region="Default">Kalau awak manusia yang sempurna macam itu…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:45.510"
        end="01:33:46.510"><span region="Default">Tak buruk jugalah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:46.510"
        end="01:33:47.340"><span region="Default">Hei!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:49.170"
        end="01:33:51.150"><span region="Default">Ariana!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:07.680"
        end="01:34:10.850"><span region="Default">Lekatkan dalam hidung dan awak akan jadi kuat.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:10.850"
        end="01:34:13.120"><span region="Default">Tak boleh! Saya tak boleh buat itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:13.120"
        end="01:34:14.570"><span region="Default">Lakukan saja.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:14.570"
        end="01:34:16.580"><span region="Default">Tiada siapa nampak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:17.460"
        end="01:34:18.730"><span region="Default">Tapi…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:18.730"
        end="01:34:22.520"><span region="Default">kertas ini dah masuk hidung Bo dan punggung Shin-chan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:22.530"
        end="01:34:23.830"><span region="Default">Bukankah itu kotor?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:23.830"
        end="01:34:26.080"><span region="Default">Bukan apa-apa jika kotor!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:26.080"
        end="01:34:28.480"><span region="Default">Ini dah bukan onigiri biasa lagi,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:28.490"
        end="01:34:31.440"><span region="Default">tapi onigiri bakar paling hebat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:31.440"
        end="01:34:32.620"><span region="Default">Betul juga…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:38.730"
        end="01:34:40.090"><span region="Default">Apa benda itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:40.100"
        end="01:34:41.130"><span region="Default">Itu Naan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:41.140"
        end="01:34:43.060"><span region="Default">Rupanya Naan kah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:50.330"
        end="01:34:51.380"><span region="Default">Eh?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:51.380"
        end="01:34:52.520"><span region="Default">Apa yang dah jadi?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:52.520"
        end="01:34:53.560"><span region="Default">Naan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:53.560"
        end="01:34:54.670"><span region="Default">Nasi?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:57.850"
        end="01:34:59.860"><span region="Default">Saya ialah chapati.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:04.030"
        end="01:35:06.890"><span region="Default">Abang! Kertas itu tercucuk pada chapati itu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:06.890"
        end="01:35:08.710"><span region="Default">Chapati yang zalim?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:09.230"
        end="01:35:12.240"><span region="Default">Chapati ialah doh daripada tepung gandum penuh dan air,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:12.240"
        end="01:35:15.620"><span region="Default">yang tidak diperam, lalu dileperkan menjadi bulat nipis dan dibakar.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:15.620"
        end="01:35:16.690"><span region="Default">Tolong ingatinya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:17.350"
        end="01:35:20.100"><span region="Default">Ia bukan terkenal di seluruh dunia.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:20.100"
        end="01:35:26.080"><span region="Default">Sudah tentu, keinginannya jadi terkenal bagi mengalahkan Naan dan juga nasi!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:26.080"
        end="01:35:27.250"><span region="Default">(Berita Terkini)</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:27.250"
        end="01:35:29.250"><span region="Default">Kami baru dapat liputan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:29.250"
        end="01:35:31.230"><span region="Default">- Apa dah jadi ini?<br/>- Ini bukannya CGI!'</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:31.230"
        end="01:35:32.480"><span region="Default">Ada apa dengan Naan gergasi ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:32.490"
        end="01:35:33.620"><span region="Default">- Itu akan<br/>- Ada apa dengan Naan gergasi ini?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:33.620"
        end="01:35:36.550"><span region="Default">- jadi satu masalah besar!<br/>- Ia mengelar dirinya sebagai chapati.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:36.550"
        end="01:35:37.990"><span region="Default">Lari!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:37.990"
        end="01:35:41.410"><span region="Default">Itu Chapati yang langsung tak dikenali di dunia ni!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:41.410"
        end="01:35:42.990"><span region="Default">Telah jumpa yang kuat!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:42.990"
        end="01:35:44.900"><span region="Default">Aku akan jadikan kau rakan seiring aku!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:49.110"
        end="01:35:51.370"><span region="Default">Chapati ini makanan dari negara India.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:51.370"
        end="01:35:54.470"><span region="Default">Ia satu hidangan yang sedap dan ia sesuai dimakan dengan kari.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:54.470"
        end="01:35:56.330"><span region="Default">Dengan guna sedikit bahan saja,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:56.330"
        end="01:35:59.780"><span region="Default">semua orang mampu buat chapati yang sedap di mana-mana dan bila-bila masa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:59.780"
        end="01:36:01.070"><span region="Default">Chapati yang lembut dan rangup.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:01.070"
        end="01:36:02.700"><span region="Default">Makanan super, chapati.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:02.700"
        end="01:36:05.070"><span region="Default">Chapati ini satu perkataan yang indah untuk dikatakan.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:05.080"
        end="01:36:07.310"><span region="Default">Ia juga buat semua rasa gembira.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:07.310"
        end="01:36:09.400"><span region="Default">- Apa dah jadi ini?<br/>- Mari eja, C-H-A-P-A-T-I</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:09.400"
        end="01:36:11.710"><span region="Default">- Kita kena buang kertas itu dari chapati!<br/>- Kami suka dan sayang Chapati!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:11.710"
        end="01:36:13.880"><span region="Default">Tapi ia terlalu tinggi di atas.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:15.280"
        end="01:36:18.090"><span region="Default">Baiklah! Mari sini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:18.730"
        end="01:36:19.800"><span region="Default">Tak boleh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:19.800"
        end="01:36:21.870"><span region="Default">Kenapa kau fikir boleh sampai lah?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:21.870"
        end="01:36:23.940"><span region="Default">Ke tepi, budak-budak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:25.150"
        end="01:36:28.480"><span region="Default">Biar kami yang jatuhkan ia dan tarik keluar kertas itu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:28.480"
        end="01:36:30.550"><span region="Default">Mari kita tamatkan di sini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:30.550"
        end="01:36:33.290"><span region="Default">Kuasa India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:40.330"
        end="01:36:41.640"><span region="Default">Mereka berjaya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:42.270"
        end="01:36:43.560"><span region="Default">Habislah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:43.560"
        end="01:36:47.060"><span region="Default">Tak guna! Kenapa?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:47.060"
        end="01:36:49.860"><span region="Default">Aku ini adalah Urufu Si Sempurna!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:49.860"
        end="01:36:52.580"><span region="Default">Lelaki terbaik di India!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:52.580"
        end="01:36:53.730"><span region="Default">Jangan buat sendiri!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:53.730"
        end="01:36:54.780"><span region="Default">Sayang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:07.880"
        end="01:37:10.430"><span region="Default">Habislah! Ada satu tangan lagi!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:13.940"
        end="01:37:15.710"><span region="Default">Maaf, kami terlambat datang!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:15.720"
        end="01:37:17.480"><span region="Default">Tuan pengetua?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:17.480"
        end="01:37:19.080"><span region="Default">Mhm Uh-huh!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:19.080"
        end="01:37:20.490"><span region="Default">Takakura Bunta!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:25.160"
        end="01:37:27.870"><span region="Default">Perangai dua orang itu macam dah berubah, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:27.870"
        end="01:37:29.890"><span region="Default">Ia satu perjalanan yang sukar ya.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:31.850"
        end="01:37:34.080"><span region="Default">Kita berjaya tangkap Chapati ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:34.080"
        end="01:37:36.380"><span region="Default">Jadi, nak buat apa sekarang?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:36.380"
        end="01:37:38.080"><span region="Default">Sekarang, mari pergi!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:41.980"
        end="01:37:43.960"><span region="Default">Jangan buat apa-apa berbahaya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:43.960"
        end="01:37:45.770"><span region="Default">- Tak nak!<br/>- Tak nak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:45.780"
        end="01:37:48.230"><span region="Default">Asal kita bersama, ke mana pun boleh pergi!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:48.230"
        end="01:37:50.110"><span region="Default">Kamu cuba nak ambil kertas itu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:50.110"
        end="01:37:52.950"><span region="Default">Betul! Ini adalah dunia kami!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:52.950"
        end="01:37:55.630"><span region="Default">Walau rasa takut… Walau menangis pun…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:55.630"
        end="01:37:57.780"><span region="Default">Jangan risau, senyumlah.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:57.790"
        end="01:37:59.500"><span region="Default">Awak bukan bersendirian.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:05.680"
        end="01:38:07.730"><span region="Default">Mari tarik kertas itu dari Chapati ini!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:07.730"
        end="01:38:10.240"><span region="Default">Dan buat dunia jadi tempat yang aman!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:10.250"
        end="01:38:11.880"><span region="Default">Kertas itu di sana!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:11.890"
        end="01:38:13.930"><span region="Default">Mari pergi, Pasukan Pertahanan Kasukabe!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:13.930"
        end="01:38:15.170"><span region="Default">Namaste!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:15.170"
        end="01:38:16.770"><span region="Default">Semangat!!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:24.580"
        end="01:38:26.310"><span region="Default">Ia tak boleh tercabut!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:26.310"
        end="01:38:28.380"><span region="Default">Mari kita sama-sama tarik!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:30.680"
        end="01:38:32.190"><span region="Default">Satu, dua!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:51.670"
        end="01:38:54.030"><span region="Default">Ia dah tercabut!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:07.690"
        end="01:39:09.710"><span region="Default">Mari makan!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:10.460"
        end="01:39:11.500"><span region="Default">Sedapnya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:11.500"
        end="01:39:14.010"><span region="Default">Ada banyak lagi itu, jadi kamu makan puas-puas.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:14.010"
        end="01:39:16.070"><span region="Default">- Chapati ini memang sedap.<br/>- Kari mana saya patut pilih.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:16.080"
        end="01:39:17.380"><span region="Default">Nak pilih mana satu?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:19.360"
        end="01:39:20.770"><span region="Default">Sedapnya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:20.780"
        end="01:39:21.960"><span region="Default">Ariana.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:21.970"
        end="01:39:23.560"><span region="Default">Awak suka lihat Goyang-goyang Penjaga Punggung?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:23.560"
        end="01:39:24.500"><span region="Default">Mestilah!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:24.510"
        end="01:39:27.000"><span region="Default">Saya suka Penjaga Punggung Ukon.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:27.000"
        end="01:39:28.600"><span region="Default">Dia nampak bergaya, kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:28.600"
        end="01:39:31.470"><span region="Default">Kegemaran saya pula<br/>Penjaga Punggung Ornithine!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:31.470"
        end="01:39:33.960"><span region="Default">Awak pula suka mana satu, Ariana?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:33.960"
        end="01:39:35.710"><span region="Default">Soalan bagus!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:35.710"
        end="01:39:37.840"><span region="Default">Bagus kau tanya soalan tu!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:37.840"
        end="01:39:39.680"><span region="Default">Kegemaran saya pula…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:40.330"
        end="01:39:43.010"><span region="Default">Semua orang ada rakan seiring mereka…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:43.630"
        end="01:39:47.060"><span region="Default">Semua ada termasuk manusia, haiwan…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:47.070"
        end="01:39:48.600"><span region="Default">Chapati pun ada juga.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:49.430"
        end="01:39:51.480"><span region="Default">Kenapa saya tiada rakan seiring?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:51.480"
        end="01:39:53.210"><span region="Default">Rakan seiring atau sahabat</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:53.210"
        end="01:39:56.570"><span region="Default">bukanlah sesuatu yang boleh diwujudkan hanya kerana kita mahu.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:58.080"
        end="01:40:00.230"><span region="Default">Bukan apa-apa bersendirian.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:00.230"
        end="01:40:01.580"><span region="Default">Jangan bandingkan diri dengan orang lain,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:01.580"
        end="01:40:02.980"><span region="Default">sebaliknya berlembutlah dengan orang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:02.980"
        end="01:40:06.970"><span region="Default">Jadilah sedikit "bodoh" dan nikmatilah perkara yang kau suka.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:06.970"
        end="01:40:10.660"><span region="Default">Jika awak boleh buat kawan tersenyum dengan ikhlas hati,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:10.660"
        end="01:40:13.160"><span region="Default">suatu hari nanti tak kisah budak atau dewasa…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:13.160"
        end="01:40:14.960"><span region="Default">Ketika awak rasa sukar nak atasi sesuatu,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:14.970"
        end="01:40:18.890"><span region="Default">mereka semula jadi ada di sisi awak.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:19.380"
        end="01:40:20.450"><span region="Default">Kan?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:20.460"
        end="01:40:21.620"><span region="Default">Uh-huh.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:21.990"
        end="01:40:24.330"><span region="Default">- Silakan.<br/>- Mari makan Chapati ini, semua.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:24.330"
        end="01:40:26.560"><span region="Default">Saya nak makan Naan pula.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:26.560"
        end="01:40:28.800"><span region="Default">- Terima kasih!<br/>- Ini adalah harinya!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:28.800"
        end="01:40:32.280"><span region="Default">Nasib baik tak ada siapa cedera, siap dapat makan capati lagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:32.290"
        end="01:40:33.690"><span region="Default">Seperti dijangka, abang.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:33.690"
        end="01:40:36.260"><span region="Default">Akhirnya, kertas yang kita cari selama ini dah ditemui.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:36.860"
        end="01:40:38.010"><span region="Default">Mana kertas itu?!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:41.780"
        end="01:40:44.300"><span region="Default">Syukurlah saya terjumpa kertas ini tadi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:44.300"
        end="01:40:47.320"><span region="Default">♪ Langsung tiada tisu tandas di India ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:47.330"
        end="01:40:49.560"><span region="Default">♪ Walau ada tisu, awak tak boleh pam tandas ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:50.170"
        end="01:40:51.580"><span region="Default">Jangan kata kertas itu…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:51.580"
        end="01:40:52.870"><span region="Default">Lap punggung awak…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:52.880"
        end="01:40:53.810"><span region="Default">Awak nak?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:53.810"
        end="01:40:55.440"><span region="Default">Tidak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:55.440"
        end="01:40:56.690"><span region="Default">Tak nak?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:56.690"
        end="01:40:58.050"><span region="Default">Tak apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:58.050"
        end="01:41:00.280"><span region="Default">Tidak!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:00.280"
        end="01:41:02.880"><span region="Default">Kertas itu terbakar.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:06.860"
        end="01:41:09.260"><span region="Default">Tak apalah, tak boleh buat apa.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:10.860"
        end="01:41:12.750"><span region="Default">Awak nak makan Chapati, pak cik?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:13.200"
        end="01:41:15.670"><span region="Default">Saya bukannya pak cik, Shinnosuke.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:15.670"
        end="01:41:21.400"><span region="Default">Nama saya Kabir Katchapapal Pakkapapal Katchapapal Pakkapapal.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:21.400"
        end="01:41:25.900"><span region="Default">Nobiru Cup Ramen, cepat masak, terus makan, dan cepat-cepat kemas balik?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:25.900"
        end="01:41:29.760"><span region="Default">Ia Kabir Katchapapal Pakkapapal Katchapapal Pakkapapal.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:30.450"
        end="01:41:32.160"><span region="Default">Cuba ulang 3 kali lagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:32.800"
        end="01:41:37.800"><span region="Default">Kabir Katchapapal Pakkapapal Katchapapal Pakkapapal!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:37.800"
        end="01:41:40.490"><span region="Default">Kabir Katchapapal Pakkapapal Katchapapal Pakkapapal!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:40.490"
        end="01:41:42.720"><span region="Default">Jadi, awak dah boleh sebutnya?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:42.720"
        end="01:41:45.650"><span region="Default">Tak, jadi ulang 3 kali lagi.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:45.650"
        end="01:41:46.610"><span region="Default">Hei!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:46.610"
        end="01:41:48.730"><span region="Default">Kabir Katchapapal Pakkapapal Katchapapal Pakkapapal…</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:07.930"
        end="01:42:12.650"><span region="Default">♪ Gelak ketawa di jalan lepas sekolah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:12.660"
        end="01:42:17.390"><span region="Default">♪ Cari jalan pintas tapi jalan berpusing pula ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:17.650"
        end="01:42:25.640"><span region="Default">♪ Langsung tak kira kegagalan satu-satu masa itu ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:26.800"
        end="01:42:31.470"><span region="Default">♪ Jumpa lagi esok, badan penuh lumpur ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:31.480"
        end="01:42:36.200"><span region="Default">♪ Dan kumpul pasir dalam poket ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:36.800"
        end="01:42:44.750"><span region="Default">♪ Semalam itu pasti menyeronokkan, kan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:45.300"
        end="01:42:48.820"><span region="Default">♪ Sejak bila? Sejak bila agaknya? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:48.820"
        end="01:42:54.110"><span region="Default">♪ Kena jadi orang yang baik ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:54.110"
        end="01:42:56.170"><span region="Default">♪ Adakah selama masa ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:56.450"
        end="01:42:58.730"><span region="Default">♪ Terikat dalam sempit yang tak dapat dielak? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:42:58.970"
        end="01:43:02.600"><span region="Default">♪ Semakin terikatkah selama ini? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:43:02.600"
        end="01:43:04.660"><span region="Default">♪ Walaupun begitu ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:43:04.660"
        end="01:43:12.000"><span region="Default">♪ Aku tak boleh kata yang aku hidup tanpa rasa ragu ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:43:12.000"
        end="01:43:16.470"><span region="Default">♪ Di sebalik lorong itu ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:43:16.750"
        end="01:43:21.440"><span region="Default">♪ Mata aku berkilauan pada alam semesta ini ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:43:21.440"
        end="01:43:26.150"><span region="Default">♪ Aku yakin bahawa aku terima ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:43:26.150"
        end="01:43:31.370"><span region="Default">♪ Pahit getir hidup bagaikan rempah rasa ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:43:31.730"
        end="01:43:36.150"><span region="Default">♪ Nak lakukan hal yang hanya sekarang boleh dibuat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:43:36.160"
        end="01:43:42.320"><span region="Default">♪ Untuk cipta suatu yang belum pernah ada ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:43:56.670"
        end="01:44:01.440"><span region="Default">♪ Bila berdepan dengan sungguh-sungguh ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:44:01.440"
        end="01:44:06.120"><span region="Default">♪ Hidup ini hanyalah rentetan kesilapan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:44:06.120"
        end="01:44:10.550"><span region="Default">♪ Di sebalik ilusi ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:44:10.850"
        end="01:44:15.480"><span region="Default">♪ Mata kita tetap bersinar ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:44:15.480"
        end="01:44:20.170"><span region="Default">♪ Setelah berkali-kali mengatasi ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:44:20.170"
        end="01:44:25.420"><span region="Default">♪ Genggaman itu jangan dilepaskan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:44:25.720"
        end="01:44:30.190"><span region="Default">♪ Di depan tangan yang terulur ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:44:30.190"
        end="01:44:36.620"><span region="Default">♪ Terlukis masa depan kita ♪</span></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
